Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,当我躺在退伍军人医院里\N{\ren}When I was lying there in the VA hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,面对着我一生最大的不幸\N{\ren}with a big hole blown through the middle of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始做一些有关于飞翔的梦\N{\ren}I started having these dreams of flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,自由地飞翔\N{\ren}I was free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  你总有醒来的一刻\N{\ren}Sooner or later, though, you always have to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你有钱的话  他们可以帮你把脊髓医好\N{\ren}They can fix a spinal, if you got the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但单靠那点退伍军人的抚恤金\N{\ren}but not on vet benefits,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不可能做到\N{\ren}not in this economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一次VA检查再加12美元\N{\ren}A VA check and 12 bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一杯咖啡\N{\ren}will get you a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是他们所称的轮候\N{\ren}I'm what they call... waitlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孟加拉虎\N{\ren}The Bengal Tiger,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,灭绝了差不多一个世纪后又回来了\N{\ren}extinct for over a century is making a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些在北京动物园的克隆品\N{\ren}These cloned tiger cubs at the Beijing Zoo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是那个物种剩下的最后几只了\N{\ren}are the latest of a number of species
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在最近五年又被克隆回来了\N{\ren}that have been cloned back into existence in the past five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我为了锻炼自己而加入了海军陆战队\N{\ren}I became a marine for the hardship. To be hammered on the anvil of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直告诉自己别人做到的事我也一定能做到\N{\ren}I told myself I can pass any test a man can pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克！杰克！杰克！杰克！\N{\ren}Jake! Jake! Jake! Jake! Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们直话直说吧\N{\ren}Let's get it straight, upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要你的同情\N{\ren}I don't want your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要一个公平的交易   你来错星球了\N{\ren}You want a fair deal, you're on the wrong planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,弱肉强食\N{\ren}The strong prey on the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是这样\N{\ren}That's just the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且没人会在意\N{\ren}And nobody does a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！   离他远点！\N{\ren}Get off! Get off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想为了应该奋斗的事而奋斗\N{\ren}All I ever wanted in my sorry-ass life was a single thing worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你知道\N{\ren}I hope you realized
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚又令你自己失去了一个顾客\N{\ren}you just lost yourself a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,娘娘腔\N{\ren}Candy-ass bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不下雨的话  我们就不训练\N{\ren}If it ain't raining, we ain't training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-那看起来不像他    -是他\N{\ren}- It doesn't look like him.  - It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是杰克.萨利？\N{\ren}You Jake Sully?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,离远点  你扫了我的兴\N{\ren}Step off. You're ruining my good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于你哥哥的\N{\ren}It's about your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找汤米.萨利\N{\ren}We're looking for Sully, T.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\ren}In there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊   汤米\N{\ren}Jesus, Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,弱肉强食\N{\ren}The strong prey on the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有个拿枪的家伙结束了他的生命\N{\ren}A guy with a knife took all Tommy would ever be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只为了他口袋里的几张钞票\N{\ren}for the paper in his wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里充满了伤感\N{\ren}The concern of the suits was touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的哥哥参与了我们一个重要投资计划\N{\ren}Your brother represented a significant investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想找你接手完成他的合同\N{\ren}We'd like to talk to you about taking over his contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们有着相同的基因组\N{\ren}And since your genome is identical to his,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们认为你可以继续他的任务\N{\ren}you could step into his shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可以这么说\N{\ren}so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会是一个新的开始\N{\ren}It'd be a fresh start
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个新的世界\N{\ren}on a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你会改头换面\N{\ren}You could do something important. You can make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬也很丰厚\N{\ren}And the pay is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,非常丰厚\N{\ren}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,汤米才是科学家  我不是\N{\ren}Tommy was the scientist, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他是那种可以飞到数光年远的外太空去\N{\ren}He was the one who wanted to get shot light-years out in space
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找真理的那种人\N{\ren}to find the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只是个笨蛋\N{\ren}Me, I was just another dumb grunt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,飞向一个自己将会后悔前往的地方\N{\ren}getting sent someplace he was gonna regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,人在低温睡眠时不会作梦\N{\ren}In cryo, you don't dream at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这种感觉不像是过了六年\N{\ren}It doesn't feel like six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,比较像是喝了五杯龙舌兰后打过一架的宿醉\N{\ren}More like a fifth of tequila and an ass-kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了吗？\N{\ren}Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我们到了  帅哥\N{\ren}Yeah, we're there, sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\ren}We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经在低温睡眠状态中\N{\ren}You've been in cryo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,躺了五年九个月二十二天\N{\ren}for five years, nine months and 22 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你会感到饥饿  也会感到虚弱\N{\ren}You will be hungry. You will be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得恶心想吐  请使用呕吐袋\N{\ren}If you feel nausea, please use the sacks provided for your convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,工作人员会非常感谢你的\N{\ren}The staff thanks you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,前面就是潘多拉星球\N{\ren}Up ahead was Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从小就听说过它  但是从没想过会去那里\N{\ren}You grew up hearing about it, but I never figured I'd be going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"女战神号"航天飞机   回复...\N{\ren}Valkyrie 1-6, copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"女战神号"航天飞机\N{\ren}Valkyrie 1-6,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在2-2-4-niner脱轨\N{\ren}you are clear for de-orbit burn at 2-2-4-niner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,收到    准备在2-2-4-niner脱轨\N{\ren}Copy, Venture Star. Go for de-orbit burn at 2-2-4-niner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上滤气面罩！ 都戴上！  戴上滤气面罩！ 都戴上！\N{\ren}- Exo-packs on! Let's go! Exo-packs on!  - Exo-packs on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得记住  没有滤气面罩\N{\ren}Remember, people, you lose that mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你将会在二十秒后昏厥  四分钟内死亡！\N{\ren}you're unconscious in 20 seconds, you're dead in four minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都不准今天给我死了！\N{\ren}Let's nobody be dead today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那会让我的报告很难看\N{\ren}Looks very bad on my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,地狱大门塔台  飞行器准备降落\N{\ren}Hell's Gate tower, this is TAV 1-6 on approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,穿越外界线  矿场进入视线\N{\ren}Crossing outer marker. Mine is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,松开安全带  拿好你们的东西\N{\ren}Harnesses off! Get your packs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我准备好  快点！动作快！\N{\ren}Put it together, let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟  准备\N{\ren}Harnesses off! One minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,舷梯落下后\N{\ren}When that ramp comes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,直接进去基地里  别停下来！\N{\ren}go directly into the base. Do not stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,直接跑过去  听我的口令！\N{\ren}Go straight inside. Wait for my mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走 走 走！  快点出去！\N{\ren}Go, go, go, go! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,继续向前！  快走  不要停下来！\N{\ren}Keep moving! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有所谓的前海军陆战队员\N{\ren}There's no such thing as an ex-Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许退役了\N{\ren}You may be out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但你永远不会忘记军人那股精神\N{\ren}but you never lose the attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  特殊人士  别让我等你\N{\ren}Let's go, special case! Do not make me wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  喔  小妞们\N{\ren}Well, well, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这群菜鸟\N{\ren}Look at all this fresh meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在地球上  这些人都是军人  陆战队员\N{\ren}Back on Earth, these guys were Army dogs, Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,为自由而战\N{\ren}fighting for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点  轮椅男！\N{\ren}Look out, hot rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里  他们只是佣兵\N{\ren}But out here they're just hired guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拿钱替私人企业办事\N{\ren}taking the money, working for the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧那家伙\N{\ren}Check this out, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃闲饭的\N{\ren}Meals on wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧  这也太扯了\N{\ren}Oh, man, that is just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,二十分钟后会有两个人有空！\N{\ren}I got two guys free in about 20 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了  我需要他们！\N{\ren}Got it! Need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已经不在堪萨斯了\N{\ren}You're not in Kansas anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是"潘多拉"星球  女士们  先生们\N{\ren}You are on Pandora, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要时时刻刻记住这一点\N{\ren}Respect that fact every second of every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果世界上真的有地狱\N{\ren}If there is a hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在游历过潘多拉后你可能会想去地狱休假\N{\ren}you might want to go there for some R&R after a tour on Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在那道围墙后面\N{\ren}Out there, beyond that fence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,任何活的东西  不论是天上飞的\N{\ren}every living thing that crawls,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是地上爬的  土里钻的\N{\ren}flies or squats in the mud
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都想把你生吞活剥地吃了\N{\ren}wants to kill you and eat your eyes for Jujubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一个原生的种族\N{\ren}We have an indigenous population of humanoids
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称其为"纳威人"\N{\ren}called the Na'vi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢在弓箭上涂上一种神经毒素\N{\ren}They're fond of arrows dipped in a neurotoxin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那玩意可以让你的心跳在一分钟内停止\N{\ren}that'll stop your heart in one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有着天生的强化碳纤维骨骼\N{\ren}And they have bones reinforced with naturally occurring carbon fiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,非常难杀死\N{\ren}They are very hard to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,做为你们的安保长官\N{\ren}As head of security,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的职责就是保障你们每一个人都活着\N{\ren}it is my job to keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是不可能的\N{\ren}I will not succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,至少不可能成功保住每一个人\N{\ren}Not with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们想活命\N{\ren}If you wish to survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就一定要有坚毅的态度\N{\ren}you need to cultivate a strong mental attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须遵守规则\N{\ren}You've got to obey the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"潘多拉规则"\N{\ren}Pandora rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,规则一\N{\ren}Rule number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都比不上这种老掉牙的训话\N{\ren}There's nothing like an old-school safety brief
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,能令人安心\N{\ren}to put your mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉 杰克  你是杰克\N{\ren}Excuse me. Excuse me. Jake! You're Jake,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗  汤米的双胞胎弟弟\N{\ren}right? Tom's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  你长得跟他一模一样\N{\ren}Wow! You look just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是诺姆.斯贝尔曼\N{\ren}Sorry, I'm Norm. Spellman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾和他一起接受"阿凡达"计划的训练\N{\ren}I went through avatar training with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是生物实验室\N{\ren}...into the bio-lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将会在这里待很久的\N{\ren}We're gonna spend a lot of time up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  你好  我是诺姆  阿凡达操作员\N{\ren}Hey! How you doing? Norm, avatar driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}- Hi. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是连结室\N{\ren}Link... Here's the link room right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在这里连结上阿凡达\N{\ren}This is where we're connecting to the avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我和诺姆会在这里\N{\ren}Me and Norm are here to drive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,远程控制这些叫"阿凡达"的生命体\N{\ren}these remotely controlled bodies called avatars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种用人类基因结合\N{\ren}And they're grown from human DNA mixed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威人的基因培育出来的生命体\N{\ren}with the DNA of the natives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  欢迎  -嘿\N{\ren}- Hey. Welcome. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到潘多拉  很高兴你们能来\N{\ren}Welcome to Pandora. Good to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\ren}- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦  他们真大\N{\ren}Damn! They got big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  在我们飞行时他们已经完全成熟了\N{\ren}Yeah, they fully mature on the flight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来本体感知模拟器运作非常顺利\N{\ren}So the proprioceptive sims seem to work really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  他们肌肉相当发达\N{\ren}Yeah, they've got great muscle tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还得花几个小时为他们准备\N{\ren}It'll take us a few hours to get them decanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不过明天你们就能操控了\N{\ren}but you guys can take them out tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的在那里\N{\ren}There's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  诺姆.斯贝尔曼博士\N{\ren}Hey. Dr. Norm Spellman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克斯.佩特尔博士 很高兴见到你\N{\ren}Dr. Max Patel. Great to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\ren}Good to meet you, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,长得很像他\N{\ren}Looks like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,长得也很像你\N{\ren}No, it looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  这是你的阿凡达了\N{\ren}This is your avatar now, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个计划的概念是\N{\ren}And the concept is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,每位操作员都能连结自己专属的阿凡达\N{\ren}that every driver is matched to his own avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的神经系统就能协调一致\N{\ren}so that their nervous systems are in tune,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,资源开发管理总署之类的\N{\ren}or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们找我的原因\N{\ren}Which is why they offered me the gig,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我能连结汤米的阿凡达\N{\ren}because I can link with Tommy's avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿凡达的造价惊人\N{\ren}which is insanely expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做对吗\N{\ren}Is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我把所有事全部录下来就对了吗？\N{\ren}I just say whatever to the video log?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对  你要习惯记录所有的事情\N{\ren}Yeah, we gotta get in the habit of documenting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,任何我们看到的  感觉到的\N{\ren}You know, what we see, what we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是科学研究的一部分\N{\ren}It's all part of the science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,详细的观察对研究很有帮助\N{\ren}And good science is good observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这样可以\N{\ren}Plus it'll help to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,让你在今后的六年里避免精神错乱\N{\ren}keep you sane for the next six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,随便啦\N{\ren}All right. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\ren}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里\N{\ren}Well, here I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,进行科学研究\N{\ren}doing science.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,操作员要出来了\N{\ren}They're coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,注意  操作员出舱中\N{\ren}Attention. Drivers coming out of link.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  天哪\N{\ren}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她的工作服呢？   谁看见她的工作服？\N{\ren}Where's the lab coat? Where's the lab coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谁拿走我的该死的香烟啦？\N{\ren}Who's got my goddamn cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  我这样子有不对吗？\N{\ren}Guys! What's wrong with this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢！\N{\ren}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝.奥古斯汀是一位传奇人物\N{\ren}Grace Augustine is a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她是阿凡达计划的带头人  她写了本书\N{\ren}She's the head of the Avatar Program. She wrote the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说那本有关潘多拉植物学的著作\N{\ren}I mean, literally wrote the book on Pandoran botany.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为她对植物的兴趣可能比对人还多\N{\ren}Well, that's 'cause she likes plants better than people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这位就是了  灰姑娘参加完舞会回来了\N{\ren}Here she is, Cinderella back from the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝我来给你介绍一下\N{\ren}Grace, I'd like you to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,诺姆.斯贝尔曼和杰克.萨利\N{\ren}Norm Spellman and Jake Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,诺姆  听说你很优秀\N{\ren}Norm. I hear good things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的纳威话学得怎么样了？\N{\ren}How's your Na'vi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,愿万灵之母....\N{\ren}May the All Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福我们的初次见面\N{\ren}...smile upon our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还不错  但太拘谨了点\N{\ren}Not bad. You sound a little formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我学了五年...\N{\ren}I studied for five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有很多东西要学\N{\ren}...but there is much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝  这位是杰克.萨利\N{\ren}Grace? This is Jake Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\ren}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是谁  我要的是你哥哥  不是你\N{\ren}Yeah, yeah. I know who you are, and I don't need you. I need your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  那位已经为这个项目\N{\ren}You know, the PhD who trained
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,培训整整三年的哲学博士？\N{\ren}for three years for this mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\ren}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这给所有人带来了巨大的麻烦\N{\ren}I know it's a big inconvenience for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在实验室受过什么训练  -解剖过一次青蛙\N{\ren}- How much lab training have you had? - I dissected a frog once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧  看吧  他们现在摆明就是要整我们\N{\ren}You see? You see? I mean, they're just pissing on us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都懒得遮掩\N{\ren}without even the courtesy of calling it rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要去找塞弗里奇 - 不  格蕾丝\N{\ren}- I'm going to Selfridge. - No, Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为这是好主意\N{\ren}I don't think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  这简直是在胡闹\N{\ren}No, man, this is such bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去给他一点颜色瞧瞧\N{\ren}I'm gonna kick his corporate butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他休想在我的部门搞鬼\N{\ren}He has no business sticking his nose in my department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上八点到这里   注意一下你的用词\N{\ren}Here tomorrow, 0800. Try and use big words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蝎子二号攻击机  这是地狱之门塔台\N{\ren}Scorpion Two-Hotel, Hell's Gate tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以从南面起飞了\N{\ren}You are cleared for south departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,使用Ｄ跑道滑行  身份确认\N{\ren}Hover taxi, Delta runway. Squawk ident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看见没？   - 看见了  长官\N{\ren}- You see that? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有  你在看监视器\N{\ren}No, you didn't. You were looking at the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱死这支球杆了  罗尼！\N{\ren}I love this putter, Ronnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱死这支球杆了\N{\ren}I love this putter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,帕克  我原本以为这只是一时的疏忽\N{\ren}Parker, you know, I used to think it was benign neglect,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我现在明白了  你根本就是在故意整我\N{\ren}but now I see that you're intentionally screwing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝  你知道  我很爱跟你小聊一下\N{\ren}Grace, you know, I enjoy our little talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要的是科学家  不是退役的陆战队员\N{\ren}I need a researcher. Not some jarhead dropout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  我倒觉得我们能找到他算很幸运的\N{\ren}Well, actually, I thought we got lucky with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 幸运   - 对\N{\ren}- Lucky? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这算哪门子的幸运？\N{\ren}How is this in any way lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,幸亏你的科学家有个双胞胎弟弟\N{\ren}Lucky your guy had a twin brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,更庆幸的是  还好他不是什么牙医师之类的\N{\ren}and lucky that brother wasn't some oral hygienist or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而是一位很有用处的陆战队员\N{\ren}A Marine we can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经指派他作你小组的护卫\N{\ren}I'm assigning him to your team as security escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在最不需要的就是\N{\ren}The last thing I need is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,多一个喜欢扣板机的白痴在我这里！\N{\ren}another trigger-happy moron out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  听着  你的任务就是要赢得\N{\ren}Look, look, you're supposed to be winning the hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那些土著的信任\N{\ren}and the minds of the natives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道不是\N{\ren}Isn't that the whole point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你那可笑的玩偶剧存在的唯一原因吗？\N{\ren}of your little puppet show?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你装扮得像他们  讲话也像他们\N{\ren}If you look like them and you talk like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们也应该就会开始信任我们\N{\ren}then they'll start trusting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们帮他们建立学校  教他们说人类语言\N{\ren}We build them a school, we teach them English,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,结果呢  这么多年过去了？\N{\ren}but after, what, how many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,关系却越搞越糟\N{\ren}Relations with the indigenous are only getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是因为你用机关枪对着他们的结果\N{\ren}Yeah, that tends to happen when you use machine guns on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好  跟我来\N{\ren}Right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  我不能\N{\ren}I can't... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们来这里的原因  超导矿石\N{\ren}This is why we're here. Unobtanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这颗小小的灰色石头\N{\ren}Because this little gray rock sells
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,每公斤价值两千万美元\N{\ren}for 20 million a kilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是唯一的原因\N{\ren}That's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个靠东西养活我们这里所有的人\N{\ren}It's what pays for the whole party.
