Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.80,0:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你知道吗？  我更喜欢现在这个样子\N{\ren}But you know what? I kind of like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.05,0:25:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以随时提醒我  外面有些什么凶险玩意\N{\ren}It reminds me every day what's waiting out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.88,0:26:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿凡达计划是个无聊的笑话\N{\ren}The Avatar Program is a bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.34,0:26:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,养了一群没用的科学家\N{\ren}Bunch of limp-dick science majors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.89,0:26:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  这无非是另一种机会\N{\ren}However, it does present an opportunity both timely and unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 后方清空！  - 清空！\N{\ren}- Clear! - Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.74,0:26:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一个伪装成阿凡达的侦查兵\N{\ren}A recon gyrene in an avatar body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.05,0:26:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个绝妙的组合\N{\ren}That's a potent mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.95,0:26:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,令我兴奋地连鸡皮疙瘩都起来了\N{\ren}Give me the goose bumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.70,0:26:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的一个陆战队员的确能给我提供不少\N{\ren}Such a Marine could provide the intel I need,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.21,0:26:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,实地的情报\N{\ren}right on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.21,0:26:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最深入的情报\N{\ren}Right in the hostiles' camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.92,0:26:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  萨利 我要你从内部了解这帮土著\N{\ren}Look, Sully. I want you to learn these savages from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.34,0:26:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你赢得他们的信任\N{\ren}I want you to gain their trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.09,0:26:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须知道怎样才能让他们就范\N{\ren}I need to know how to force their cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.93,0:26:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,或是如何逼他们就范  如果他们不肯屈服\N{\ren}or hammer them hard if they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我还是奥古斯汀小组的成员吗？\N{\ren}Am I still with Augustine?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.84,0:26:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,台面上是\N{\ren}On paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以和那些科学家一起做研究\N{\ren}Yeah, you walk like one of her science pukes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.74,0:26:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以跟他们闲话家常\N{\ren}you quack like one,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.94,0:26:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是向我报告\N{\ren}but you report to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.94,0:26:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做得到吗  小子？\N{\ren}Can you do that for me, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.28,0:27:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  长官\N{\ren}Hell, yeah, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.57,0:27:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就对了\N{\ren}Well, all right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.38,0:27:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子  我会照顾自己人的\N{\ren}Son, I take care of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.34,0:27:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿到我需要的东西后\N{\ren}You get me what I need,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等你回来时我会让你重新站起来\N{\ren}I'll see to it you get your legs back when you rotate home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,用你自己的腿\N{\ren}Your real legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.85,0:27:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来很诱人  长官\N{\ren}That sounds real good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.61,0:27:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 连结准备就绪！ - 同步率40%\N{\ren}- Link's ready! - Phase-Iock 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.94,0:27:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不许出声  让诺姆负责说话\N{\ren}Just keep your mouth shut and let Norm do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.11,0:27:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,第五阶段融合完成  同步率90%\N{\ren}I have five congruencies. Phase-Iock 90%.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.74,0:27:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,三号舱准备就绪\N{\ren}Link three ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.75,0:27:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我要进去了\N{\ren}All right, I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.32,0:28:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,斯塔姆兽就在你右面\N{\ren}Sturmbeest herd coming up on your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.12,0:28:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了！  谢谢\N{\ren}Got it! Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.45,0:28:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙就像是公牛  但又带有些温柔\N{\ren}Looks like a bull, a dozen cows and some juveniles.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.13,0:29:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉引擎  我们会在这里停留一会\N{\ren}Shut it down. We're gonna stay a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.97,0:29:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-诺姆  你的背包 -背包\N{\ren}- Norm! Your pack. - Pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.39,0:29:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你就待在飞机旁吧\N{\ren}Stay with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.11,0:29:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个拿着枪的白痴就够了\N{\ren}One idiot with a gun is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.81,0:29:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了算  博士\N{\ren}You the man, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.06,0:30:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,潘多拉狐猴  没有攻击性的\N{\ren}Prolemuris. They're not aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.07,0:30:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松点  陆战队的  你搞得我也紧张了\N{\ren}Relax, Marine. You're making me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.78,0:30:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们如何知道我们来到这里？\N{\ren}So, how will they know we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.45,0:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定他们现在正在监视着我们\N{\ren}I'm sure they're watching us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.25,0:30:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里曾经是我们建的学校\N{\ren}This was our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.29,0:30:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这里只是一个贮藏库了\N{\ren}Now it's just... storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孩子都是非常聪明的\N{\ren}The kids were so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.05,0:30:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,热衷于学习\N{\ren}Eager to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.43,0:30:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的人类语言甚至不用我教也学得很快\N{\ren}They picked up English faster than I could teach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.31,0:30:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那么拿一些酸碱检测器\N{\ren}So, we'll take a couple of these Ph monitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.56,0:30:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和探泥针\N{\ren}...and a soil probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.14,0:31:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的小黄色箱子 有个旧的显微镜\N{\ren}That little yellow case back there. The old microscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.07,0:31:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个\N{\ren}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.24,0:31:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  对  我很爱这个\N{\ren}Oh, yeah. I love this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.36,0:31:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那些刺蝠把它们都搞到地上了\N{\ren}The stingbats knocked them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.12,0:31:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都希望能有孩子回到这里 再读读它们\N{\ren}I keep hoping someone will come back in and read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.42,0:31:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么不回来？\N{\ren}Why don't they come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.05,0:31:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,奥玛蒂卡亚族部落\N{\ren}The Omaticaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.13,0:31:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经精通了我们的语言\N{\ren}learned as much about us as they needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.31,0:31:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么事？\N{\ren}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.52,0:31:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你还打算用这装备来帮我们吗？\N{\ren}Are you going to help us with this gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.44,0:31:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有很多事要忙\N{\ren}We've got a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.12,0:32:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别停下  诺姆 - 你们俩跟紧了！\N{\ren}- Keep moving, Norm. - Keep up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.50,0:32:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么就开始啦 - 扫描中\N{\ren}- And here I go. - Scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.51,0:32:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这么快{？\r}\N{\fnArial Narrow\fs12\shad0\1c&H0076EE&\b1\i1}Wow! It's that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.93,0:32:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很惊人  是吧？   - 是啊\N{\ren}- Amazing, isn't it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.10,0:32:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是信号传导\N{\ren}So, that is signal transduction from this root
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.98,0:32:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从这个树根传到旁边的那个树根\N{\ren}to the root of the tree next to it. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.15,0:32:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该采集一个样本\N{\ren}we should take a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.69,0:32:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好  样本\N{\ren}Okay. Sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,反应速度那么快  我觉得这里可能有电流\N{\ren}You know, it's probably electrical, based on the speed of the reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.36,0:32:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,诺姆  你的口水污染到样本了\N{\ren}Norm, you've contaminated the sample with your saliva.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.79,0:32:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  对不起\N{\ren}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.36,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再采一个样本\N{\ren}So, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.72,0:33:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪  别开枪  你会把它惹毛的\N{\ren}Don't shoot. Don't shoot, you'll piss him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.31,0:33:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经把它惹毛了\N{\ren}It's already pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.10,0:33:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  它皮太厚 子弹打不穿  相信我\N{\ren}Jake, that armor's too thick. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.86,0:33:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是在宣示它的地盘\N{\ren}It's a territorial threat display.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.75,0:33:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别跑  否则他会冲上来的\N{\ren}Do not run, or he'll charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:34:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要做啥  跟它跳舞吗？\N{\ren}So, what do I do, dance with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.83,0:34:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,待在原地别动\N{\ren}Just hold your ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.01,0:34:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊  看你有什么能耐？\N{\ren}Yeah? Come on! What you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.51,0:34:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊  看谁厉害  这就对了\N{\ren}Oh, yeah. Who's bad? That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.48,0:34:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就对了  畜牲\N{\ren}Yeah, that's what I'm talking about, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.44,0:34:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对啦  滚回去找你的妈咪吧\N{\ren}That's right, get your punk ass back to mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.11,0:34:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些能耐啊  快滚吧\N{\ren}Yeah? Yeah, you got nothing. You keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.11,0:34:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要不再多叫几个同伴过来？\N{\ren}Yeah, and why don't you bring back some of your friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.20,0:34:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\ren}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.13,0:34:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么应付这种  跑  还是不跑？\N{\ren}So what about this one? Run? Don't run? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.05,0:35:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跑  当然要跑啦\N{\ren}Run! Definitely run!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.57,0:38:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天只能到此为止了\N{\ren}I'm gonna have to call it, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.95,0:38:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上校有命令不许夜间飞行的\N{\ren}We're not allowed to run night ops. Colonel's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.58,0:38:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  博士  他只能靠自己撑到早上了\N{\ren}I'm sorry, Doc, he's just gonna have to hang on till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.91,0:38:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他撑不到明天早上的\N{\ren}He won't make it till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.44,0:40:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我没那时间陪你们耗整晚\N{\ren}I don't have all goddamn night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.24,0:40:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊！  来啊！\N{\ren}Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.27,0:42:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  别扔\N{\ren}Hey, wait. Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这下好了\N{\ren}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.00,0:43:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你可能听不懂我在说什么\N{\ren}Look, I know you probably don't understand this,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.64,0:43:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是谢谢你\N{\ren}but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.02,0:43:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.44,0:43:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这真让人印象深刻\N{\ren}That was pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.65,0:43:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没有你  我早就没命了 这真是\N{\ren}I would have been screwed if you hadn't come along. It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  你要去那里？\N{\ren}Hey, wait a second. Hey, where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.29,0:43:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我\N{\ren}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走慢点\N{\ren}Just... Hey, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.33,0:43:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想谢谢你  帮我杀了那些东西\N{\ren}Look, wait up, I just wanted to say thanks for killing those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:44:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死 - 不要道谢\N{\ren}- Damn! - Don't thank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.47,0:44:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,杀戮不需要道谢\N{\ren}You don't thank for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.39,0:44:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在太可悲了 非常可悲\N{\ren}This is sad. Very sad only.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.27,0:44:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧  我很抱歉\N{\ren}Okay. Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.19,0:44:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我做了什么  我很抱歉\N{\ren}Whatever I did, I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.53,0:44:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你的错  它们本来不应该死的\N{\ren}All this is your fault. They did not need to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.53,0:44:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我的错  它们攻击我\N{\ren}My fault? They attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.78,0:44:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么我倒成了坏人?\N{\ren}How am I the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.70,0:44:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你的错!   - 哎  喔\N{\ren}Your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.83,0:44:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就是你的错! - 别激动  别激动\N{\ren}- Your fault! - Easy. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.62,0:44:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像个婴儿  只会乱叫  不知所措\N{\ren}You're like a baby. Making noise, don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.37,0:44:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别激动\N{\ren}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.13,0:44:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好\N{\ren}Fine. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.71,0:44:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你这么爱你的森林朋友\N{\ren}If you love your little forest friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.38,0:44:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不干脆让它们杀了我\N{\ren}why not let them just kill my ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.22,0:44:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么逻辑?\N{\ren}What's the thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.81,0:44:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要救你吗?\N{\ren}Why save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.22,0:44:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对  为什么要救我?\N{\ren}Yeah. Yeah, why save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.94,0:44:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一颗坚强的心\N{\ren}You have a strong heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.03,0:45:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无畏无惧\N{\ren}No fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.74,0:45:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很愚昧  像个孩子一样无知\N{\ren}But stupid! Ignorant like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.04,0:45:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我像个孩子  那么\N{\ren}Well, if I'm like a child, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.13,0:45:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那或许你该教教我\N{\ren}Look, maybe you should teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.42,0:45:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们天空人永远都学不会  你们不用心去感受\N{\ren}Sky People cannot learn. You do not See.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.72,0:45:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那教教我怎么感受啊\N{\ren}Well, then teach me how to See.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.63,0:45:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有人能够教你如何用心去感受 - 哇\N{\ren}- No one can teach you to See. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.47,0:45:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  别这样  我们不能多聊聊吗?\N{\ren}Look, come on, can't we talk?
