Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.72,0:45:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  回去吧\N{\ren}No! Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.50,0:46:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.05,0:46:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,回去\N{\ren}Go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.90,0:46:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.72,0:46:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这\N{\ren}What...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.68,0:46:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是什么?\N{\ren}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.52,0:46:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂之树的种子\N{\ren}Seeds of the Sacred Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.56,0:47:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,非常纯洁的灵魂\N{\ren}Very pure spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.34,0:47:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事？\N{\ren}What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.38,0:47:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\ren}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.93,0:47:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\ren}Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.22,0:47:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去那里？\N{\ren}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.07,0:47:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\ren}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.29,0:48:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\N{\ren}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.13,0:48:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\ren}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.70,0:48:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.53,0:48:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住手  大家冷静一点\N{\ren}Calm people, calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.17,0:48:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰  你这是在干什么？\N{\ren}What are you doing, Tsu'tey?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.46,0:48:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这些恶魔禁止到这里来\N{\ren}These demons are forbidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.18,0:48:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出现神迹了\N{\ren}There has been a sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.51,0:48:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,必须交由查希克决定\N{\ren}This is a matter for the Tsahik.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.68,0:49:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把他带走\N{\ren}Bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.19,0:49:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?\N{\ren}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.11,0:49:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们走\N{\ren}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.20,0:49:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了?\N{\ren}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.70,0:49:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿!\N{\ren}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.89,0:50:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\ren}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.06,0:50:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到你\N{\ren}...I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.58,0:50:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地球人\N{\ren}This creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.29,0:50:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么把他带到这里来？\N{\ren}...why do you bring him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.83,0:50:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本要杀了他\N{\ren}I was going to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.50,0:50:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我看见艾娃显现神迹\N{\ren}...but there was a sign from Eywa.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.50,0:50:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过\N{\ren}I have said...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.59,0:50:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不许带梦行者到这里来\N{\ren}...no dreamwalker will come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.34,0:50:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么？\N{\ren}What's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.68,0:51:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这个外星人的臭味真令我作呕\N{\ren}His alien smell fills my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.60,0:51:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么？\N{\ren}Hey, what's he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.68,0:51:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲在决定是否要杀了你\N{\ren}My father is deciding whether to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.56,0:51:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲  很高兴见到您  先生\N{\ren}Your father. It's nice to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.19,0:51:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,放开这个生物  谁都别动他！\N{\ren}Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.82,0:51:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看看这个外星人\N{\ren}I will look at this alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.36,0:51:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我母亲\N{\ren}That is Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.66,0:51:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她是查希克  能够解读艾娃神谕的人\N{\ren}She is Tsahik. The one who interprets the will of Eywa.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.50,0:51:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是艾娃？\N{\ren}Who's Eywa?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.71,0:51:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？\N{\ren}What are you called?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.38,0:51:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克.萨利\N{\ren}Jake Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.68,0:51:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么来到这里？\N{\ren}Why did you come to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.41,0:51:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来学习的\N{\ren}I came to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.85,0:51:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾经试过教导其他天空人\N{\ren}We have tried to teach other Sky People.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.90,0:51:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是自满的人是很难去接受别人的教导\N{\ren}It is hard to fill a cup which is already full.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.74,0:52:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点都不自满  相信我\N{\ren}Well, my cup is empty, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.28,0:52:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去问奥古斯汀博士\N{\ren}Just ask Dr. Augustine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.86,0:52:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是一位科学家\N{\ren}I'm no scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.04,0:52:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那你又是什么？\N{\ren}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.75,0:52:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾是个陆战队员  就是\N{\ren}I was a Marine. A...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.83,0:52:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一名"锅盖头族"的战士\N{\ren}A warrior of the Jarhead clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.92,0:52:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一个战士！\N{\ren}A warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.26,0:52:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我能轻易就宰了他！\N{\ren}I could kill him easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.84,0:52:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我能轻易就宰了他！   不行！\N{\ren}I could kill him easily!  No!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.55,0:52:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次遇到梦行者战士\N{\ren}This is the first warrior dreamwalker...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.76,0:52:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,以前从未遇见过\N{\ren}...we have seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.72,0:52:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要多加了解他\N{\ren}We need to learn more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.02,0:52:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女儿\N{\ren}My Daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.98,0:52:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你将负责教导他学习我们文化\N{\ren}...you will teach him our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.36,0:52:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,学习我们的语言和我们的生活方式\N{\ren}...to speak and walk as we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.82,0:52:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么是我教  这不公平\N{\ren}Why me? That's not fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.24,0:52:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么决定了\N{\ren}It is decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.82,0:52:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿会教你我们的生活方式\N{\ren}My daughter will teach you our ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.46,0:52:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好好学吧  杰克.萨利\N{\ren}Learn well, Jakesully.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.84,0:53:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们再看看  你是否还有药可治\N{\ren}Then we will see if your insanity can be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.36,0:53:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\ren}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.86,0:53:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦站起来了\N{\ren}Please don't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.49,0:53:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,借过\N{\ren}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.16,0:53:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\ren}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.42,0:53:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你好吗？\N{\ren}Hey, how you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.72,0:53:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.26,0:53:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊  我还不知道你的名字\N{\ren}You know, I don't even know your name.
