Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.66,0:54:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你   妮特丽\N{\ren}It's nice to meet you, Neytiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.28,0:54:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\ren}It's nice.
