Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.09,0:55:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事了  你没事了\N{\ren}You're okay. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.55,0:55:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  你投入得就像只吸血扁虱\N{\ren}Damn! You were dug in like a tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.56,0:55:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的阿凡达安全吗   - 他很安全  博士\N{\ren}- Is the avatar safe? - Yeah, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.23,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们绝对不会相信我去了哪里\N{\ren}And you are not gonna believe where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.94,0:55:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后看到的是这个海军陆战队员的背影\N{\ren}The last thing we see is this Marine's ass
