Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.25,0:55:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而那头怒气沖沖的闪雷兽紧追着他的屁股跑\N{\ren}with this angry thanator coming after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.16,0:55:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这可不是一般人学得来的 - 真了不起\N{\ren}- Hey, it's not something you can teach. - That is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.24,0:55:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么原因我也无法理解\N{\ren}You know, for reasons I cannot fathom,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.62,0:55:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么奥玛蒂卡亚族选择了你\N{\ren}the Omaticaya have chosen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.49,0:55:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷帮了我们一个大忙\N{\ren}God help us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.29,0:55:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,锅盖头族！\N{\ren}"Jarhead clan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.38,0:55:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们居然信了！\N{\ren}And it worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.77,0:55:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在跟他们是一家人了\N{\ren}Hey, I'm practically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.51,0:55:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想了解我\N{\ren}They're gonna study me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.73,0:55:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而我要学习如何成为他们的一份子\N{\ren}I have to learn to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.01,0:55:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这就叫先发制人  小子\N{\ren}That's called taking the initiative, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.68,0:55:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望能多十个像你这么能干的\N{\ren}I wish I had 10 more like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.21,0:55:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  萨利  萨利\N{\ren}Look, Sully. Sully.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.31,0:56:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,试着查出那些蓝猴子到底想要什么\N{\ren}Just find out what the blue monkeys want.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.48,0:56:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\ren}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.15,0:56:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给他们医疗  教育  道路\N{\ren}I mean, we try to give them medicine, education, roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.32,0:56:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没用  他们只爱玩泥巴\N{\ren}But no, no, no, they like mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.24,0:56:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那倒是无所谓  不过问题是\N{\ren}And that wouldn't bother me, it's just that they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.78,0:56:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你能 谁来弄一下    第十二区\N{\ren}Hey, can you... Can somebody just... Sector 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.62,0:56:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好  走  走  走  停  停\N{\ren}Okay, go, go, go, stop. Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.83,0:56:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,够了  停下！  那是 天哪！\N{\ren}Rich, stop! That's... Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.04,0:56:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们那该死的部落刚好就位于\N{\ren}Their damn village happens to be resting on the richest unobtanium deposit
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,方圆两百公里之内  最丰富的矿区上\N{\ren}within 200 klicks in any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.35,0:56:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看看那些矿藏！\N{\ren}I mean, look at all that cheddar!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.35,0:56:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁能说服他们离开呢？  - 你说呢\N{\ren}- Well, who gets them to move? - Guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.77,0:56:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他们不想离开呢？\N{\ren}What if they won't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.54,0:56:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌他们一定会离开的\N{\ren}I'm betting that they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.82,0:56:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好  嘿  听着\N{\ren}Okay, okay, okay, okay, hey. Look. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.36,0:56:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了那些土著的确会很令人难堪\N{\ren}Killing the indigenous looks bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.28,0:56:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是比起那些媒体的丑闻\N{\ren}but there's one thing that shareholders hate
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.23,0:56:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,股东们更在意的只有一件事\N{\ren}more than bad press,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.12,0:56:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是难看的季度报表\N{\ren}and that's a bad quarterly statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.98,0:57:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这些规矩不是我定的\N{\ren}I didn't make up the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.37,0:57:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以帮我找一个能够让他们搬离这里的方法\N{\ren}So just find me a carrot that'll get them to move,
