Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.98,0:57:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但莫娅是精神领袖  就像萨满\N{\ren}But she's the spiritual leader. Like a shaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.23,0:57:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\ren}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.90,0:57:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏泰 - 苏泰\N{\ren}- T'su'tey. - Tsu'tey.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.20,0:57:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 苏泰 - 他将是下一任的酋长\N{\ren}- Tsu'tey. - He'll be the next clan leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.95,0:57:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妮特丽 - 她将是下一任的查希克\N{\ren}- Neytiri. - She'll be the next Tsahik.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.50,0:57:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将会配对\N{\ren}They become a mated pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.50,0:57:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那艾娃是谁？   - 艾娃是谁？\N{\ren}- So who's this Eywa? - Who's Eywa?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.67,0:57:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们唯一的神  创造出许多生命的造物者\N{\ren}Only their deity. Their goddess, made up of all living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.34,0:57:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,无所不知的神\N{\ren}Everything they know!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.76,0:57:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是接受过训练就不会问这种问题了\N{\ren}You'd know this if you had any training whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.97,0:57:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁正在和酋长的女儿约会\N{\ren}Who's got a date with the chief's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.39,0:57:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  那是\N{\ren}Come on. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.64,0:58:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个别闹了   把这里搞得托儿所似的\N{\ren}Knock it off. It's like kindergarten around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.85,0:58:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽曾经是我最好的学生\N{\ren}Neytiri was my best student.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.89,0:58:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她和她姐姐   Sylwanin\N{\ren}She and her sister, Sylwanin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.98,0:58:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很棒的女孩\N{\ren}Just amazing girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也跟Sylwanin有个约会哦\N{\ren}I got a date with Sylwanin too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.99,0:58:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经死了\N{\ren}She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.91,0:58:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  乡村生活可是很早就开始的\N{\ren}Let's go. Village life starts early.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.66,0:58:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,别做什么太愚蠢的事\N{\ren}Don't do anything unusually stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.35,0:58:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,乖  小伙子\N{\ren}Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.31,0:58:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,潘多拉烈马是母的\N{\ren}Pale is female.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.36,0:58:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  乖  小姑娘\N{\ren}Okay. Easy, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.56,0:59:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是"萨黑鲁"  心灵连接\N{\ren}That is shahaylu. The bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.48,0:59:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感受她\N{\ren}Feel her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.86,0:59:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感受她的心跳  她的呼吸\N{\ren}Feel her heartbeat. Her breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.99,0:59:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,感受它健壮的腿\N{\ren}Feel her strong legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.24,0:59:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以告诉它要做什么\N{\ren}You may tell her what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.66,0:59:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,用心告诉它\N{\ren}Inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.83,0:59:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  告诉它要去那里\N{\ren}For now, say where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.75,0:59:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,往前！\N{\ren}Forward!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.61,1:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该离开这里的\N{\ren}You should go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.17,1:00:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  你会想我的\N{\ren}No, you'd miss me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.15,1:00:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会说人类语言\N{\ren}I knew you could speak English.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.03,1:00:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个外星人根本学不会任何东西\N{\ren}This alien will learn nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.62,1:00:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,连颗石头都比他知道的多\N{\ren}...a rock sees more...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.62,1:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧他那副德性\N{\ren}...look at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.76,1:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,再试一次\N{\ren}Again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.92,1:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真想要攻击这里的话\N{\ren}If you want to hit this thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.26,1:00:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那将会非常麻烦\N{\ren}it's gonna be complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.43,1:00:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的扫瞄器无法显示它内部的结构\N{\ren}Your scan doesn't show the internal structure.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.01,1:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,外围是一圈柱状物\N{\ren}There's an outer row of columns.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.14,1:00:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,非常结实  这里还有第二圈\N{\ren}Real heavy duty. There's a secondary ring here,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.98,1:00:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,里面还有一圈\N{\ren}and an inner ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.36,1:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,核心部分则是像螺旋形的结构\N{\ren}There's a core structure like a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.48,1:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是为何他们能在树内上下移动\N{\ren}That's how they move up and down.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.19,1:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要准确扫瞄每根支柱的构造\N{\ren}We're gonna need accurate scans on every column.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.11,1:01:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\ren}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.57,1:01:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对于结构你还有什么要提供吗？\N{\ren}What else can you tell us about the structure?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.28,1:01:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这第二圈支柱也是支撑结构\N{\ren}I'm guessing this secondary ring, that's also load-bearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.66,1:01:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要去那里   - 离开这里\N{\ren}- So where are we going? - Getting out of Dodge.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.50,1:01:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会让帕克和夸奇插手这里的事\N{\ren}I'm not about to let Selfridge and Quaritch micro-manage this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.76,1:01:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,二十六号哨站有一个移动的连结室\N{\ren}There's a mobile link up at Site 26 we can work out of,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.09,1:01:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在山里继续研究\N{\ren}way up in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.80,1:01:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利路亚山？\N{\ren}The Hallelujah Mountains?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.18,1:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 你说的是真的吗？\N{\ren}- That's right. - Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.56,1:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 太棒了\N{\ren}- Yeah. - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.98,1:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的潘多拉悬浮山  你\N{\ren}The legendary floating mountains of Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.37,1:01:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,又没听说过了吧？\N{\ren}Heard of them?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.17,1:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快到了\N{\ren}We're getting close.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.13,1:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  看看我的仪器吧\N{\ren}Yeah, look at my instruments.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.84,1:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们进入电磁旋涡了\N{\ren}Yep. We're in the Flux Vortex.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.88,1:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始目视飞行\N{\ren}We're VFR from here on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.22,1:02:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是目视飞行？\N{\ren}What's VFR?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.18,1:02:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就是用你的眼睛来看路\N{\ren}Means you gotta see where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.64,1:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但我什么都看不见啊\N{\ren}You can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.78,1:02:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  很夸张吧\N{\ren}Exactly. Ain't that a bitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.04,1:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\N{\ren}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.72,1:02:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧你们那副表情\N{\ren}You should see your faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.12,1:03:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您搭乘潘多拉航空\N{\ren}Thank you for flying Air Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.55,1:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么维持着他们漂浮？\N{\ren}So what does hold them up?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.35,1:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝向我解释过\N{\ren}Grace explained it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.56,1:03:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是由于某种磁悬浮的影响\N{\ren}Some kind of maglev effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.56,1:03:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为unobtanium是一种类似超导的物质\N{\ren}Because unobtanium is a superconductor... or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.96,1:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临营地\N{\ren}Welcome to camp.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.38,1:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以  我睡这里   - 好恶心\N{\ren}- So, this is my bunk. - This stuff is nasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.35,1:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 诺姆  你睡下面 - 好\N{\ren}- Norm, go under. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.47,1:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝什么都知道\N{\ren}Grace didn't miss a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.41,1:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,楚迪  你睡上面\N{\ren}Trudy, you'll take the top one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.02,1:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道我跟上校暗中往来\N{\ren}She knew I was talking to the Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.52,1:04:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但她目前还需要我才能让她重回到部落\N{\ren}But I had what she needed, a way back in with the clan,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.23,1:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她现在对我还算客气\N{\ren}so she's playing nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.94,1:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  杰克  左转\N{\ren}All right. Jake, hang a left.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.49,1:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你使用最后面一台连接舱\N{\ren}You'll be in the link at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.91,1:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一号舱  比尤拉 她是这里最稳定的一台\N{\ren}Unit one. Beulah. She's the least glitchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.21,1:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,酷毙了\N{\ren}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.42,1:05:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要盯着她的眼睛看\N{\ren}Do not look in her eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.89,1:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伊卡兰不是马\N{\ren}Ikran is not horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.77,1:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦完成了"萨黑鲁"\N{\ren}Once shahaylu is made,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.48,1:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,伊卡兰终身只会跟随一名猎人\N{\ren}ikran will fly with only one hunter in the whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.75,1:06:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要想成为"塔龙纽"  也就是猎人\N{\ren}To become taronyu, hunter,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.58,1:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须选择你自己的伊卡兰\N{\ren}you must choose your own ikran
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.87,1:06:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,同时它也要选择你\N{\ren}and he must choose you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.72,1:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么时候   - 等你准备好的时候\N{\ren}- When? - When you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.14,1:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好  影像日记第十二号\N{\ren}Okay. This is video log 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.48,1:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,时间是晚上九点三十二分\N{\ren}Time's 2132.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.61,1:07:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我非得要现在做这些吗  我真的很想睡了\N{\ren}Do I have to do this now? I really need to get some rack.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.03,1:07:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  就现在  趁热打铁\N{\ren}No, now. When it's fresh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.53,1:07:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  地点  棚屋\N{\ren}Okay, location, shack,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.37,1:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,日子开始搞混在一起了\N{\ren}and the days are starting to blur together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.83,1:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威语很难学  但是 你知道\N{\ren}The language is a pain, but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.09,1:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得就像拆装武器一样\N{\ren}I figure it's like field-stripping a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.58,1:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要反覆地练习  反覆地练习\N{\ren}Just repetition, repetition.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.38,1:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 眼睛 - 眼睛\N{\ren}- Navi.  - "Nari."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.05,1:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 眼睛  -眼睛\N{\ren}- Nari.  - "Narrri"!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.39,1:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛\N{\ren}Narrri!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.60,1:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用力一点  用力一点\N{\ren}Txurnì'ul. Stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.23,1:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽称呼我为"斯康"\N{\ren}Neytiri calls me skxawng. It means moron.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.23,1:07:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是笨蛋\N{\ren}This is a very important part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.74,1:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在诺姆对我的态度也大有好转\N{\ren}Norm's attitude has improved lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.30,1:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到你\N{\ren}I see you. I see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.95,1:08:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威语的看见不仅仅是用眼睛看见\N{\ren}But it's not just, "I'm seeing you in front of me,"
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.41,1:08:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而是用心灵感应到你\N{\ren}it's "I see into you. I See you."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.16,1:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,能和他友好相处是很不错\N{\ren}It's good he's back on board,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.67,1:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但他也认为我是个笨蛋\N{\ren}but he thinks I'm a skxawng, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.91,1:08:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"我接受你  我理解你"\N{\ren}"I'm accepting you. I understand you."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.41,1:08:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你得搞清楚差别？好吗\N{\ren}So you gotta get this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.50,1:08:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你得快点  好了吗？  出发\N{\ren}I gotta run! Okay? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.25,1:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的脚变得越来越强壮\N{\ren}My feet are getting tougher.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.30,1:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我一天跑得比一天远\N{\ren}I can run farther every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.71,1:08:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须相信我的身体才能去做任何困难的事\N{\ren}I have to trust my body to know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.93,1:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  看到没有\N{\ren}Yeah! Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.48,1:08:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 妈的！\N{\ren}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.02,1:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每天都在观察森林小径\N{\ren}Every day it's reading the trails,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.30,1:08:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,像水坑中的足迹\N{\ren}the tracks at the waterhole,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.94,1:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,察觉最微小的气味和声音\N{\ren}the tiniest scents and sounds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.74,1:08:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她总是提到一种会流动的能量  万物的灵魂\N{\ren}She's always going on about the flow of energy, the spirits of animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.29,1:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望最终测验的时候\N{\ren}I really hope this tree-hugger crap
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.84,1:08:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这些锁碎的题目\N{\ren}isn't on the final.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.09,1:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是单靠眼睛看和双手触摸就可以理解的\N{\ren}This isn't just about eye-hand coordination out there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.80,1:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须仔细倾听她所说的一切\N{\ren}You need to listen to what she says.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.59,1:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,透过她的眼睛  去感受这片森林\N{\ren}Try to see the forest through her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.80,1:09:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  这可是我的影像日记\N{\ren}Excuse me. This is my video log here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.82,1:09:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着妮特丽学习  如果不学快一点就完蛋了\N{\ren}With Neytiri, it's learn fast or die.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.66,1:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在开玩笑的吧\N{\ren}You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.86,1:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我说服莫娅让格蕾丝来到部落\N{\ren}I talked Mo'at into letting Grace into the village.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.03,1:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你们  都长这么高了\N{\ren}Look how big you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.74,1:10:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,自从她的学校关闭后  这是她第一次回来\N{\ren}It's the first time since her school was closed down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.74,1:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你变得好漂亮啊\N{\ren}You are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.73,1:10:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡觉 陆战队的\N{\ren}Come on, Marine.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.54,1:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着用心体会这种微妙的关系\N{\ren}I'm trying to understand this deep connection
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.34,1:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,人和森林的心灵感应\N{\ren}the people have to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.01,1:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她说能量就如同某种连结网路\N{\ren}She talks about a network of energy
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.68,1:11:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,万物都是息息相关的\N{\ren}that flows through all living things.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.14,1:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她说  生命都是由万物所生成的\N{\ren}She says all energy is only borrowed,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.35,1:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天  生命将回到最原始的起点\N{\ren}and one day you have to give it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.06,1:12:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天进入了阿凡达16个小时了\N{\ren}You were in 16 hours today.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.40,1:12:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的体重不断在减少\N{\ren}You're still losing weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.91,1:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\ren}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.62,1:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要去睡一会儿   - 给我回来\N{\ren}- I gotta get some sleep. - Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.58,1:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,祝好胃口\N{\ren}Bon appétit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.42,1:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我杀生了\N{\ren}Today I made a kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.88,1:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还吃了它\N{\ren}And we ate it. At least,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.06,1:12:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于知道他们的食物来源了\N{\ren}I know where that meal came from.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.09,1:12:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是另一个身体\N{\ren}Other body.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.70,1:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也要照顾这一个身体的 知道吗？\N{\ren}You need to take care of this body. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.35,1:12:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知道了吗？   我们吃了它 - 好的  好的\N{\ren}- Get it? Let's eat it.  - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.64,1:12:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来  我来帮你把\N{\ren}Here. I'll make it easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.10,1:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把袋子给我\N{\ren}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.44,1:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你真邋遢  - 谢谢夸奖\N{\ren}- You look like crap.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.02,1:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你做事太极端了\N{\ren}You're burning way too hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.86,1:12:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,把这狗屎弄走\N{\ren}Get rid of this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.78,1:12:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你可以继续诉说我了\N{\ren}And then you can lecture me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.78,1:12:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在   我要跟你讲 作为你的老板\N{\ren}Now, I'm telling you, as your boss,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.95,1:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,或者以后还有可能变为朋友的人  我告诉你\N{\ren}and as someone who might even consider being a friend someday
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.37,1:13:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你坐下来待会儿\N{\ren}to take some down time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.87,1:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你吃了它吧\N{\ren}Eat this, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.13,1:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我吧 我了解你的艰难\N{\ren}Trust me, I... learned the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.98,1:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那间学校发生过什么事  格蕾丝？\N{\ren}What did happen at the school, Grace?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.74,1:13:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽的姐姐   Sylwanin\N{\ren}Neytiri's sister, Sylwanin,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.62,1:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间再也没来上学\N{\ren}stopped coming to school.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.45,1:13:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她对于森林的砍伐非常气愤\N{\ren}She was angry about the clear-cutting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.50,1:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后有一天\N{\ren}And one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.73,1:13:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她和另一对年轻的猎人跑了进来\N{\ren}she and a couple of other young hunters came running in
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.96,1:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全身都绘上了东西\N{\ren}all painted up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.17,1:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们烧了一台推土机\N{\ren}They had set a bulldozer on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.13,1:13:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那些士兵跟踪他们一直到学校\N{\ren}I guess they thought I could protect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.81,1:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们以为我可以保护他们\N{\ren}The troopers pursued them to the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.81,1:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在门口把Sylwanin打死了\N{\ren}They killed Sylwanin in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.06,1:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就在妮特丽面前\N{\ren}Right in front of Neytiri.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.48,1:14:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始向其他孩子开枪\N{\ren}And then shot the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.44,1:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然大部分孩子都被我带走了\N{\ren}I got most of the kids out.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.99,1:14:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们再也没有来了\N{\ren}But they never came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.46,1:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\ren}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.05,1:14:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一个科学家不能有任何偏见\N{\ren}A scientist stays objective.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.68,1:14:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能被情绪而驱动\N{\ren}We can't be ruled by emotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.60,1:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我花了10年心血在那间学校\N{\ren}But I put 10 years of my life into that school.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.81,1:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫我sa'nok\N{\ren}They called me sa'nok.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.65,1:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲\N{\ren}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.73,1:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲\N{\ren}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.15,1:15:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那伤痛跟随着我到了现在\N{\ren}That kind of pain reaches back through the link.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.02,1:15:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到你\N{\ren}I see you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.23,1:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟\N{\ren}...Brother
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.90,1:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\ren}...and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.23,1:15:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的灵魂将与艾娃同在\N{\ren}Your spirit goes with Eywa.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.65,1:15:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体将留在这里\N{\ren}Your body stays behind...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.78,1:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我们的一部分\N{\ren}...to become part of The People.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.12,1:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一箭毙命\N{\ren}A clean kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.96,1:15:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经准备好了\N{\ren}You are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.11,1:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,学习驾驭伊卡兰  我们称之为"女妖翼兽"\N{\ren}Learning to ride an ikran, we call them banshees,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.57,1:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是每一位猎人都必经的考验\N{\ren}is the test every young hunter has to pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.37,1:16:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想要完成这项考验\N{\ren}But to do that,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.70,1:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要先抵达女妖翼兽的栖息地\N{\ren}you gotta go where the banshees are.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.54,1:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呜哇\N{\ren}Oo-rah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.24,1:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢？\N{\ren}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.60,1:18:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克.萨利先来\N{\ren}Jakesully will go first.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.43,1:19:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你要选择你的伊卡兰 你要用内心去感受\N{\ren}Now you choose your ikran. This you must feel inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.35,1:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果它也选择你的话\N{\ren}If he also chooses you,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.60,1:19:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的动作要快  像我示范的那样\N{\ren}move quick like I showed.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.39,1:19:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有一次机会  杰克\N{\ren}You will have one chance, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.27,1:19:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要怎么知道它选上我\N{\ren}How will I know if he chooses me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.52,1:19:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它会试图杀掉你\N{\ren}He will try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.65,1:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\ren}Outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.34,1:20:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来跳舞吧\N{\ren}Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.89,1:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋快没命了\N{\ren}That moron's going to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.62,1:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕  战士\N{\ren}Don't be afraid, warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.58,1:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快点缔结关系\N{\ren}Make the bond!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.38,1:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.38,1:21:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\ren}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.52,1:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,萨黑鲁  杰克\N{\ren}Shahaylu, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.53,1:21:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,萨黑鲁！\N{\ren}Shahaylu!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.87,1:22:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点！\N{\ren}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.63,1:22:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  没错  你是我的了？\N{\ren}Yeah, that's right. You're mine. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.94,1:22:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次飞行认定关系  你不能等\N{\ren}First flight seals the bond. You cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.40,1:22:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想着飞   - 飞\N{\ren}- Think, "Fly!" - Fly?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.21,1:22:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的！\N{\ren}God damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.88,1:22:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  完了！\N{\ren}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.60,1:23:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  直飞！\N{\ren}Shut up and fly straight!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.03,1:23:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这还差不多  向左转！\N{\ren}That's it. Bank left!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.66,1:23:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,保持水平  这就对了\N{\ren}Level out! That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.96,1:23:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  杰克.萨利！\N{\ren}Jake Sully!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.07,1:24:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！\N{\ren}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.16,1:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧！\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.92,1:24:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,耶  宝贝  我成功了！\N{\ren}Yeah, baby, I got this!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.68,1:24:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  该死的！\N{\ren}Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.23,1:24:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我骑马的技术可能不怎么样\N{\ren}I may not be much of a horse guy,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.18,1:24:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但骑这个我可是天生的高手\N{\ren}but I was born to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.81,1:24:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\ren}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.86,1:24:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-我像这样飞过来  你像这样 - 好\N{\ren}- I came like this. This you. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.03,1:24:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,顺着风转弯  可以转的更快\N{\ren}I turn. I feel the wind. I turn very strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.79,1:24:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  我转得太僵硬了\N{\ren}Look, yeah, see, I banked so hard...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.09,1:25:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂之树\N{\ren}The Tree of Souls.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.52,1:25:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他们最神圣的地方\N{\ren}It's their most sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.48,1:25:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看那漩涡磁流  还有这些图像？\N{\ren}See the Flux Vortex in these false color images?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.40,1:25:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那东西把我的仪器弄挂的\N{\ren}Yeah, that's what messes up my instruments.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.57,1:26:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一些很有趣的生物现象\N{\ren}There is something really interesting going on in there biologically.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.49,1:26:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想冒死去取点样本\N{\ren}I would die to get samples.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.16,1:26:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,外人可是严格禁止进入的\N{\ren}Outsiders are strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.08,1:26:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子真幸运\N{\ren}You lucky swine.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.78,1:27:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\ren}Hell, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.95,1:27:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\N{\ren}Hell, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.30,1:27:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾是一个冷血的空中猎人 从空中播撒死亡\N{\ren}I was a stone-cold aerial hunter. Death from above.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.35,1:27:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但问题是  你也有可能是别人的猎物\N{\ren}Only problem is, you're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.31,1:28:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,俯冲！\N{\ren}Dive!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.17,1:28:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！ 快走！\N{\ren}Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.55,1:28:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\ren}Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.31,1:29:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人管它叫做"狮鹰翼兽"\N{\ren}Our guys call it a Great Leonopteryx.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.81,1:29:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,它是托鲁克  最终阴影\N{\ren}It is Toruk. Last Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.61,1:29:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理  她会是你死亡前看到的最后影像\N{\ren}Yeah, right. It's the last one you ever see.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.33,1:29:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的曾曾祖父是托鲁克玛克托\N{\ren}My grandfather's grandfather was Toruk Macto.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.79,1:29:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"魅影骑士"\N{\ren}Rider of Last Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.96,1:29:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他骑这个\N{\ren}He rode this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.05,1:29:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,托鲁克选择了他\N{\ren}Toruk chose him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.01,1:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我们族人的传说\N{\ren}It has only happened five times
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.14,1:29:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,历史上只发生过五次\N{\ren}since the time of the First Songs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.97,1:29:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那还真是悠久 - 是的\N{\ren}- That's a long time. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.68,1:29:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,魅影骑士非常伟大\N{\ren}Toruk Macto was mighty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.39,1:30:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾在苦难时期把所有部落凝聚起来\N{\ren}He brought the clans together in a time of great sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.23,1:30:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,每个纳威人都听过这个故事\N{\ren}All Na'vi people know the story.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.28,1:30:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每一件事好像都颠倒了过来\N{\ren}Everything is backwards now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.64,1:30:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿那里才是真实的世界\N{\ren}Like out there is the true world
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.62,1:30:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而这里反倒变成了一场梦\N{\ren}and in here is the dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.31,1:30:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,很难相信日子才过了三个月\N{\ren}It's hard to believe it's only been three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.06,1:30:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎记不起以前的生活\N{\ren}I can barely remember my old life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.07,1:30:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至忘了我是谁\N{\ren}I don't know who I am anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.67,1:31:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没在森林里迷失了自我吧\N{\ren}Haven't gotten lost in the woods, have you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.68,1:31:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,距离你上一次的报告\N{\ren}Your last report was
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.14,1:31:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,已经是两个星期前的事了\N{\ren}more than two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.81,1:31:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我都开始怀疑你是不是放弃了！\N{\ren}I'm starting to doubt your resolve!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.90,1:31:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来  是时候终止这项任务了\N{\ren}The way I see it, it's time to terminate the mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.48,1:31:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我可以完成\N{\ren}No, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.44,1:31:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经完成了\N{\ren}You already have.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.99,1:31:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了我很有用的情报\N{\ren}You give me good, usable intel.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.28,1:31:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫灵魂之树的地方\N{\ren}This Tree of Souls place.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.95,1:31:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我有这个把柄在手\N{\ren}Yeah, I got them by the balls
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.78,1:31:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,作战时就可以逼他们就范\N{\ren}with that when this turns into a shit fight,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.41,1:31:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,战争不可避免\N{\ren}which it will. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.12,1:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候归队了\N{\ren}Now it's time to come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.59,1:31:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\ren}By the way,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.96,1:31:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以重新站起来了\N{\ren}you gonna get your legs back.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.84,1:32:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经帮你取得了公司的同意  全都搞定了\N{\ren}Yeah. I got your corporate approval. It's a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.51,1:32:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚就可以搭船回家了\N{\ren}Gonna have you on a shuttle tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.05,1:32:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个说话算话的人\N{\ren}I'm a man of my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.77,1:32:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须把它完成\N{\ren}I gotta finish this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.81,1:32:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有最后一件事\N{\ren}There's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.07,1:32:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一个仪式  这是成为纳威人的最后阶段\N{\ren}Ceremony. It's the final stage of becoming a man.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.53,1:32:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果做到了  我就会成为他们的一份子\N{\ren}If I do it, I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.16,1:32:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就会信任我\N{\ren}And they'll trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.58,1:32:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就可以跟他们谈搬迁的事宜\N{\ren}And I can negotiate the terms of their relocation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.39,1:32:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你最好把它搞定  下士\N{\ren}Well, then, you'd better get it done, Corporal.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.33,1:33:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威人说  每个人出生后都会经过两次洗礼\N{\ren}The Na'vi say that every person is born twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.33,1:33:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次\N{\ren}The second time is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.51,1:33:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是当你在族人面前取得一个永久的地位\N{\ren}when you earn your place among The People forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.26,1:33:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是奥玛蒂卡亚族之子\N{\ren}You are now a son of the Omaticaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.77,1:33:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我们的一份子了\N{\ren}You are part of The People.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.32,1:34:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来  来\N{\ren}Come. Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.96,1:34:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们族人祈祷的地方\N{\ren}This is a place for prayers to be heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.30,1:34:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候你的祈祷也会灵验\N{\ren}And sometimes answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.02,1:34:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们称这些树为"奥特拉亚莫克力"\N{\ren}We call these trees Utraya Mokri.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.73,1:34:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,声音之树\N{\ren}The Tree of Voices.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.48,1:35:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先灵之声\N{\ren}The voices of our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.67,1:35:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以听见他们\N{\ren}I can hear them.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.17,1:35:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  他们还活着\N{\ren}They live, Jake,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.84,1:35:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,与艾娃同在\N{\ren}within Eywa.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.43,1:35:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是奥玛蒂卡亚族人了\N{\ren}You are Omaticaya now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.02,1:35:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以拥有属于你自己的弓箭\N{\ren}You may make your bow from the wood of Hometree.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.65,1:35:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,然后选择一位女子\N{\ren}And you may choose a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.86,1:35:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多好女人\N{\ren}We have many fine women.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.03,1:35:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,尼娜唱歌最好听\N{\ren}Ninat is the best singer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.91,1:35:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想要尼娜\N{\ren}But I don't want Ninat.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.13,1:36:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,佩拉是位好猎人\N{\ren}Beyral is a good hunter.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.76,1:36:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对  她真是位好猎人\N{\ren}Yeah, she is a good hunter.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.93,1:36:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已经选择了\N{\ren}I've already chosen.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.18,1:36:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这位女子也必须选择我\N{\ren}But this woman must also choose me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.69,1:36:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她早也已经选择好了\N{\ren}She already has.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.75,1:37:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你在一起了  杰克\N{\ren}I am with you now, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.25,1:37:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们此生永不分离\N{\ren}We are mated for life.
