Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.90,1:38:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克！\N{\ren}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.95,1:38:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Okay.
