Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.22,1:38:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次洗澡是什么时候\N{\ren}And when was the last time you took a shower?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.55,1:39:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不需要洗澡   -天哪  陆战队的\N{\ren}- I don't need a shower. - Jesus, Marine.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.77,1:39:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\ren}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.82,1:39:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克！  醒醒啊！   杰克！  醒醒啊！\N{\ren}Jake! Wake up! Jake! Wake up!
