Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.34,1:39:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么了！    -有个纳威人\N{\ren}- What? - I got a native
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.51,1:39:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对着机器乱吼乱叫  他挡到我的路了\N{\ren}doing the funky chicken here. He's blocking my blade.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.56,1:39:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,继续开  他会闪开的\N{\ren}Well, keep going. He'll move.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.77,1:39:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人必须明白  我们是不会停的\N{\ren}These people have to learn that we don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.74,1:39:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,继续  走  走  走\N{\ren}Come on, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.36,1:39:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来！  嘿！\N{\ren}Stop! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.65,1:39:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快走！  快走！\N{\ren}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.95,1:39:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧  看到没有？  他闪开了吧\N{\ren}There, see? He moved.
