Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.60,1:40:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克！ - 妮特丽！\N{\ren}- Jake! - Neytiri!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.44,1:40:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这边  快跑！\N{\ren}Here, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.01,1:41:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,定格  就在那里\N{\ren}Freeze it right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.18,1:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拉近  放大\N{\ren}Scale up. Enhance.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.26,1:41:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\ren}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.31,1:41:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信\N{\ren}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.85,1:41:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我找个飞行员来 - 是  长官\N{\ren}- Get me a pilot. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.78,1:41:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰  将带领我们战斗\N{\ren}Tsu'tey will lead the war party.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.54,1:41:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么做\N{\ren}Stop please!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.33,1:41:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会使事情变更糟\N{\ren}This will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.58,1:41:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有你说话的地方\N{\ren}You do not speak here!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.42,1:41:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要打得他们满地找牙\N{\ren}We will strike them in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.01,1:41:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰  不要这样做\N{\ren}Tsu'tey! Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.31,1:41:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-你   -听着  兄弟\N{\ren}- You! - Listen. Brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.32,1:42:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你跟这女人交配了？   - 喔  坏了\N{\ren}- You mated with this woman? - Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.74,1:42:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗？\N{\ren}Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.24,1:42:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在艾娃的面前互定终身  已成定局了\N{\ren}We are mated before Eywa. It is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.83,1:42:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟  听我说\N{\ren}Brother, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.08,1:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去攻击天空人\N{\ren}Do not attack the Sky People.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.73,1:42:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你那样做会害死很多同胞的\N{\ren}Many Omaticaya will die if you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.92,1:42:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你才不是我的兄弟！\N{\ren}You are not my brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.42,1:42:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也不是你的敌人！\N{\ren}And I am not your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.84,1:42:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的敌人就在外面  他们的火力很强大！\N{\ren}The enemy is out there, and they are very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.97,1:42:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,前进！  前进！  前进！\N{\ren}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.98,1:42:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我跟他们谈 -不用谈了\N{\ren}- I can talk to them. - No more talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.48,1:42:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰\N{\ren}Tsu'tey!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.11,1:42:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奥玛蒂卡亚族人  我是你们的一份子\N{\ren}I am Omaticaya. I am one of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.83,1:42:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有说话的权利\N{\ren}And I have the right to speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.71,1:42:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些事情要说\N{\ren}I have something to say...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.92,1:43:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们每一个人说\N{\ren}...to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.42,1:43:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话在我心里已经憋了很久\N{\ren}The words are like stones in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.85,1:43:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我很抱歉  别！别！不要！ 住手！\N{\ren}Sir, I'm sorry. No, no, no! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.85,1:43:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能干扰连线！\N{\ren}You can't interrupt a link in progress!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.31,1:43:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这么做很危险\N{\ren}It's very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.27,1:43:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\ren}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.65,1:43:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕\N{\ren}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.07,1:43:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-等等   -你给我趴下\N{\ren}- Wait! - Stay down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.57,1:43:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好  听着\N{\ren}Okay. Look...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.91,1:43:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被派到这里来\N{\ren}I was sent here to...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.87,1:43:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吧\N{\ren}You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.46,1:43:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他只不过是个使用假身的魔鬼 他不能活着\N{\ren}It is a demon in a false body.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.81,1:44:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你他妈的疯了吗   - 你太过分了\N{\ren}- Are you out of your goddamn mind? - You crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.65,1:44:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,把这家伙给我带走\N{\ren}Wheel this meat out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.53,1:44:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  到底发生了什么事？\N{\ren}Jake! What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.33,1:44:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我真失望  小子\N{\ren}You let me down, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.08,1:44:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了  你\N{\ren}So, what,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.88,1:44:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里找到了个土著女朋友\N{\ren}you find yourself some local tail
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.92,1:44:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就忘了你是站在哪一边的了？\N{\ren}and you just completely forget what team you're playing for?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.22,1:44:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,帕克  还有时间挽回局面\N{\ren}Parker, there is time to salvage the situation.
