Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.70,1:45:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-老天  -我说的不是\N{\ren}- for Christ's sake! - I'm not talking
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.12,1:45:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那些灵异的巫术\N{\ren}about some kind of pagan voodoo here. I'm talking about something real,
