Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.80,1:45:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,用来解释生物与森林之间的关系\N{\ren}Something measurable in the biology of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.38,1:45:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什么东西？\N{\ren}Which is what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.92,1:45:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们所知\N{\ren}What we think we know
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.30,1:45:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在树与树根之间都有着某种\N{\ren}is that there is some kind of electrochemical communication
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.76,1:45:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,类似电流的讯息传递\N{\ren}between the roots of the trees,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.97,1:45:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像神经细胞组织那样\N{\ren}like the synapses between neurons.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.27,1:45:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,每一棵树之间都有着成千成万个不同的连结点\N{\ren}And each tree has ten-to-the-fourth connections to the trees around it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.94,1:45:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,潘多拉星球有上亿万棵树\N{\ren}And there are ten-to-the-twelfth trees on Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.98,1:45:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想就是指这里有很多树\N{\ren}Which is a lot, I'm guessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.32,1:45:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这比人脑还要复杂\N{\ren}It's more connections than the human brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.91,1:45:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗  这像是一种网路\N{\ren}Get it? It's a network.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.49,1:45:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一种全球网路  纳威人可以登录进去\N{\ren}It's a global network, and the Na'vi can access it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.62,1:45:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以上传和下载讯息  甚至储存\N{\ren}They can upload and download data. Memories.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.17,1:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚毁掉的就是一个网站\N{\ren}At sites like the one you just destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.50,1:45:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\ren}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.80,1:45:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底在外面嗑了什么东西\N{\ren}What the hell have you people been smoking out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.55,1:45:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过只是一些该死的树而已！\N{\ren}They're just goddamn trees!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.39,1:45:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,帕克  你要搞清楚\N{\ren}You need to wake up, Parker.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.79,1:46:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你才给我搞清楚\N{\ren}No. You need to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.18,1:46:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球的资源不是在地下\N{\ren}The wealth of this world isn't in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.05,1:46:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在我们的周围\N{\ren}It's all around us.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.77,1:46:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威人知道这一点  他们会誓死捍卫它\N{\ren}The Na'vi know that, and they are fighting to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.57,1:46:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想跟他们共同享有这个世界\N{\ren}If you want to share this world with them,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.49,1:46:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要去了解他们\N{\ren}you need to understand them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.95,1:46:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我要说  我们已经了解得够多了\N{\ren}I'd say we understand them just fine,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.03,1:46:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这还真得多亏了杰克\N{\ren}thanks to Jake here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.37,1:46:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  博士  过来看看\N{\ren}Hey, Doc, come take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.91,1:46:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会放弃他们的家园\N{\ren}They're not gonna give up their home.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.96,1:46:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会接受任何条件\N{\ren}They're not gonna make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.67,1:46:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要什么   清淡啤酒\N{\ren}For what? Lite beer?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.55,1:46:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝色牛仔裤？\N{\ren}And blue jeans?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.34,1:46:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本就不需要我们的东西\N{\ren}There's nothing that we have that they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.14,1:46:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所做的一切根本是在浪费时间\N{\ren}Everything they sent me out here to do is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.11,1:46:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会离开家园树的\N{\ren}They're never gonna leave Hometree.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.40,1:46:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,既然达不成协议\N{\ren}So, since a deal can't be made,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.98,1:47:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这事就变得简单多了\N{\ren}I guess things get real simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.62,1:47:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  谢了  我真的很兴奋\N{\ren}Jake, thanks. I'm getting all emotional.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.16,1:47:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋到我都想给你一个热吻\N{\ren}I might just give you a big wet kiss.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.48,1:47:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说一下状况  莱尔\N{\ren}Talk to me, Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.53,1:47:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看来他们首先是用女妖翼兽来进攻的\N{\ren}It looks like they hit it with banshees first.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.20,1:47:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那个角被浸透过没有？\N{\ren}See the angle's steep?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.12,1:47:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们放火烧了AMP装甲\N{\ren}They set the ampsuit on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.50,1:47:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,驾驶员成烤土豆了\N{\ren}Driver's toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.21,1:47:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,其他队员呢？\N{\ren}The rest of the squad?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.13,1:47:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,6具尸体  全都在这里了\N{\ren}Six bodies. That's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.51,1:47:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,设备损失\N{\ren}The equipment's totaled.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.55,1:48:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\ren}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.18,1:48:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽量把伤害降到最低\N{\ren}I'll do it with minimal casualties to the indigenous.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.44,1:48:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会先用催泪瓦斯把他们给赶走\N{\ren}I'll drive them out with gas first.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.19,1:48:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这应该会人道一点\N{\ren}It'll be humane.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.40,1:48:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大概吧\N{\ren}More or less.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.57,1:48:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  开始干吧\N{\ren}All right, let's pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.87,1:48:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点准备好  出发\N{\ren}Come on, people. Let's get it packed, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.58,1:48:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你知道的 他从来都没想过我们会成功\N{\ren}You know, they never even wanted us to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.58,1:48:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们故意用推土机去铲别人的圣地\N{\ren}They bulldozed a sacred site on purpose
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.02,1:48:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,惹毛别人\N{\ren}to trigger a response.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.21,1:48:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后编造借口  发动战争\N{\ren}Just fabricating this war
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.75,1:48:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,去得到他们想要的东西\N{\ren}to get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.51,1:48:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,掠夺就是这样\N{\ren}This is how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.18,1:48:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当别人拥有你想要的东西\N{\ren}When people are sitting on shit that you want,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.56,1:48:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你就视他们为敌人\N{\ren}you make them your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.32,1:48:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后顺理成章的把东西抢过来\N{\ren}Then you're justified in taking it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.69,1:48:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,夸奇上校刚刚召集了武装直升机\N{\ren}Quaritch is rolling the gunships.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.89,1:48:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去攻击家园树\N{\ren}He's gonna hit Hometree.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.07,1:48:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\ren}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.53,1:49:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,奥古斯汀博士  你不能到这里来\N{\ren}Dr. Augustine! You cannot be up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.01,1:49:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\ren}Back off!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.79,1:49:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,帕克  等等  停下\N{\ren}Parker. Wait. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.86,1:49:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是人  你却要\N{\ren}These are people you're about to...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.58,1:49:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  不  不  - 我叫你走开！\N{\ren}- No. No, no, no, no. - I said back off!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.75,1:49:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是一群浑身叮满苍蝇住在树上的野蛮人！\N{\ren}They're fly-bitten savages that live in a tree!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.25,1:49:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗  看看四周\N{\ren}All right? Look around!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.05,1:49:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太清楚你是怎么想\N{\ren}I don't know about you,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.44,1:49:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我看到了很多很多的树  他们可以搬走！\N{\ren}but I see a lot of trees! They can move!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.84,1:49:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙能不能\N{\ren}Can you guys just please...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.79,1:49:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  首长\N{\ren}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.39,1:49:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,家园树里有很多家庭  有小孩  有婴儿\N{\ren}There are families in there. There are children. Babies.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.97,1:49:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要杀小孩吗？\N{\ren}Are you gonna kill children?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.35,1:49:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会真的想这么做  相信我\N{\ren}You don't want that kind of blood on your hands. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.35,1:49:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去说服他们\N{\ren}Just let me try to talk them out.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.56,1:49:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们信任我\N{\ren}They trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.32,1:49:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快点准备  我们立刻出发\N{\ren}Calibrate fast. We're going in, right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.82,1:49:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,三号   四号就绪\N{\ren}Calibrating three and four.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.82,1:49:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-启动程序  -倒数三十秒\N{\ren}- Run sequence. - Initiating. Thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.16,1:49:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我给你一个小时\N{\ren}Listen to me. You've got one hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.96,1:49:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想让你的女朋友一起陪葬的话\N{\ren}Unless you want your girlfriend in there when the ax comes down,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.63,1:49:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫他们赶紧滚蛋  就一个小时\N{\ren}you get them to evacuate. One hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.34,1:50:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\ren}Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.64,1:50:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲\N{\ren}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.68,1:50:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,埃图康  我有话要说\N{\ren}Eytukan, I have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.02,1:50:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请听他说\N{\ren}Listen!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.48,1:50:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧  杰克.萨利\N{\ren}Speak, Jakesully.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.31,1:50:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,灾难就要降临了\N{\ren}A great evil is upon us...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.61,1:50:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,天空人正往这里来\N{\ren}The Sky People are coming...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.73,1:50:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毁家园树\N{\ren}...to destroy Hometree.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.70,1:50:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们  天空人马上就要来了\N{\ren}Look, tell them they're gonna be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.70,1:50:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不离开就会没命\N{\ren}You have to leave, or you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.54,1:50:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\ren}Are you certain of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.29,1:50:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是他们派我来学习你们的文化\N{\ren}Look, they sent me here to learn your ways
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.17,1:50:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以便有一天我可以传达这个讯息的时候\N{\ren}so one day I could bring this message
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.58,1:50:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们才会相信我\N{\ren}and that you would believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.01,1:50:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  你在说什么？\N{\ren}What are you saying, Jake?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.91,1:50:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你早就知道会发生这种事\N{\ren}You knew this would happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.85,1:50:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\ren}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.40,1:51:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  一开始我只是奉命行事\N{\ren}Look, at first it was just orders,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.36,1:51:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但后来  一切都变了\N{\ren}and then everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.74,1:51:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗   我爱上了\N{\ren}Okay? I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:07.20,1:51:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上了这片森林  爱上了奥玛蒂卡亚族人\N{\ren}I fell in love with the forest and with the Omaticaya people.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.66,1:51:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\ren}And with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.08,1:51:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我当初信任你    - 我爱上了你\N{\ren}- I trusted you. - With you. With you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.00,1:51:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是那么的相信你    - 请你现在相信我\N{\ren}- I trusted you! - Trust me now, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.22,1:51:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会成为我们的一分子\N{\ren}You will never be one of The People!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.72,1:51:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不应该    - 我们试着阻止他们了\N{\ren}- I shouldn't have... - We tried to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.60,1:51:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妮特丽  别这样   - 永远不会\N{\ren}Neytiri, please! Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.56,1:51:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们绑起来\N{\ren}Bind them.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.36,1:51:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快点走吧\N{\ren}Leave now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.65,1:51:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须离开  他们就要到了\N{\ren}You have to go. They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.83,1:52:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一分钟后抵达目标\N{\ren}Time on target, one mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.09,1:52:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  目标进入视线\N{\ren}Copy. We have a visual.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.13,1:52:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  保持航向  方位0-3-0\N{\ren}Roger that. Stay on heading 030.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.26,1:52:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明白  方位0-3-0\N{\ren}Roger, 030.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.40,1:52:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 赶快逃进森林里去   -他们快到了！\N{\ren}- Run to the forest! - They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.07,1:52:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会摧毁这个地方\N{\ren}They will destroy this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.91,1:52:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽  你得立刻离开\N{\ren}Neytiri, you must go now!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.66,1:52:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快逃进森林里去   快走\N{\ren}Run to the forest! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.33,1:52:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跑  跑\N{\ren}Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.67,1:52:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要犹豫了\N{\ren}Have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.19,1:53:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不  该死的  快走啊！\N{\ren}No! God damn it, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.15,1:53:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,骑上伊卡兰\N{\ren}Take the ikran...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.69,1:53:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从空中发动攻击\N{\ren}...attack from above.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.53,1:53:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是他妈的一颗大树\N{\ren}That is one big damn tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.25,1:53:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个  看来我们的谈判失败了\N{\ren}Well, well, well. I'd say diplomacy has failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.42,1:53:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦  各位  开工吧！\N{\ren}All right, people, let's get this done!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.59,1:53:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要所有的催泪瓦斯弹都对准了入口\N{\ren}I want every gas round you got right in the front door.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.51,1:53:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,了解  CS.40催泪瓦斯弹准备发射\N{\ren}Roger. CS.40's going hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.93,1:53:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-开火 -发射\N{\ren}- Fire. - Firing.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.57,1:53:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,中了   你真是神枪手\N{\ren}Bingo. Mighty good shooting, ace.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.53,1:54:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  他们开火了\N{\ren}Sir, they've opened fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:02.08,1:54:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在开玩笑的吧\N{\ren}You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.39,1:54:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这些野蛮人怎么还搞不清楚状况\N{\ren}These dumb bastardsain't getting the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.97,1:54:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给他们一点颜色瞧瞧\N{\ren}All right, let's turn up the heat.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.72,1:54:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-改用燃烧弹！  -改用燃烧弹\N{\ren}- Switch incendiaries! - Switching incendiaries.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.73,1:54:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\ren}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.15,1:54:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.45,1:54:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快到森林里去\N{\ren}Get everyone to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.58,1:54:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,蟑螂就是这么驱散的\N{\ren}And that's how you scatter the roaches.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.55,1:54:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽\N{\ren}Neytiri!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.43,1:55:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得想办法离开  他们要炸掉树干了！\N{\ren}We gotta move! He's gonna blow the columns!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.56,1:55:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\ren}My God!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.41,1:55:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莫娅  不要！   - 如果你是我们的一分子\N{\ren}- Mo'at! No! - Lf you are one of us,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.29,1:55:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请你帮帮我们\N{\ren}help us.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.39,1:55:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所有单位  改用导弹\N{\ren}All call signs, switch missiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.56,1:55:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把导弹都给我对准西边树干\N{\ren}Give me HE's at the base of the west columns.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.93,1:55:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\ren}This way!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.31,1:55:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士小队改用导弹\N{\ren}Rider section, switch missiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.27,1:55:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一号准备完成 - 二号完成\N{\ren}- One's good. - Two's rocks up.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.32,1:55:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三号完成   - 耶  尝尝这个！\N{\ren}- Three's up. - Yeah, baby, get some!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.40,1:55:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥机  战机待命中\N{\ren}Charlie Oscar, Gunrunner standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.74,1:56:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把它轰垮  - 准许发射\N{\ren}- Bring it down. - Cleared hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.20,1:56:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝  快点！\N{\ren}Come on, Grace, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.42,1:56:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下  快趴下！\N{\ren}Down! Head down!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.59,1:56:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快  快  趴下\N{\ren}Come on, come on! Down!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.60,1:56:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 命中  - 确实命中目标\N{\ren}- Solid hits. - Solid rocks on target.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.68,1:56:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\ren}Screw this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.10,1:56:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唉！  你在搞什么啊\N{\ren}Hey! What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.19,1:56:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是为了干这种混账事来这里的！\N{\ren}I didn't sign up for this shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.66,1:56:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,重复  火力全开\N{\ren}Repeat. Ripple fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.08,1:57:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑！  快！  快！\N{\ren}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.74,1:58:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  回来  回来\N{\ren}No, no, get back! Back!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.21,1:58:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快  走  走\N{\ren}Come on! Come on, move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.80,1:59:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  各位  今晚的庆功宴算我的\N{\ren}That's good work, people. First round's on me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:14.10,1:59:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,全体回航吧\N{\ren}Let's boogie.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.77,1:59:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,飞龙突击艇左转弯  返航回基地\N{\ren}Dragon coming left, heading home.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.65,1:59:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,炮艇机左转弯\N{\ren}Gunrunner coming left.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.65,1:59:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 雷电小队收到  - 骑士小队收到\N{\ren}- Thunder copies. - Rider section copies.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.78,1:59:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！\N{\ren}Father!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.72,1:59:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,女儿\N{\ren}Daughter...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.22,1:59:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着  我的  弓箭\N{\ren}take... my... bow.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.43,2:00:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,保护族人\N{\ren}Protect The People.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.28,2:00:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽！\N{\ren}Neytiri!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.58,2:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起  对不起 - 走开\N{\ren}- I'm sorry. I'm sorry. - Get away.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.96,2:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,给我滚开！\N{\ren}Get away!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.34,2:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远远的！\N{\ren}Get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.55,2:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,永远别再回来！\N{\ren}Never come back!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.82,2:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把机器停了\N{\ren}Pull the plug.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.95,2:00:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能！  不  你不能这么做！\N{\ren}No, you can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:54.86,2:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这么做！\N{\ren}You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.62,2:00:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冷静！  冷静下来！    - 不！  拜托！\N{\ren}- Calm down! Calm down! - No! Please!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.80,2:01:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本梦想成为带来和平的战士\N{\ren}I was a warrior who dreamed he could bring peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.77,2:01:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但很残酷的是  你终究必须回到现实\N{\ren}Sooner or later, though, you always have to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.48,2:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走！\N{\ren}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.78,2:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把他放下！\N{\ren}Put him down!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.74,2:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个杀人凶手！\N{\ren}You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.13,2:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过得如何啊  兄弟  好久不见\N{\ren}What's going on, brother? Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.30,2:02:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\ren}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.72,2:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我个人认为这些环保叛徒根本没资格享受牛排\N{\ren}Personally, I don't feel these tree-hugging traitors deserve steak.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.51,2:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,牛排  太扯了  让我瞧瞧\N{\ren}They get steak? That's bullshit. Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.89,2:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么  趴下\N{\ren}Yeah. You know what that is. Down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.52,2:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 楚迪 - 五体投地\N{\ren}- Trudy! - All the way down.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.44,2:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克斯\N{\ren}Max!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:59.74,2:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,楚迪  发动直升机！  快！\N{\ren}Trudy, fire up the ship! Go!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:02.83,2:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着\N{\ren}Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.01,2:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安全  快走   - 给你\N{\ren}- Clear. Come on. - Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.03,2:03:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克斯  你留下来\N{\ren}Max, stay here.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.01,2:03:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个能信任的内应\N{\ren}I need someone on the inside I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.99,2:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好  走吧\N{\ren}Okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.09,2:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\N{\ren}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.22,2:03:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  宝贝\N{\ren}Come on, baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:57.51,2:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,上校？  长官？  我这里有状况\N{\ren}Colonel? Sir? I got a situation here.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.93,2:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大力神1-6号未经许可擅自启动引擎\N{\ren}It's Samson 1-6. Unauthorized engine start.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.02,2:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,三!\N{\ren}Three!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.15,2:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.32,2:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上滤气面罩！\N{\ren}Mask on!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.24,2:04:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有毒气  有毒气  有毒气！\N{\ren}Gas, gas, gas!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.70,2:04:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在向我们开火！  快点走！\N{\ren}I'm taking fire! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.21,2:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手！  快  大家都进来了  我们走吧！\N{\ren}Grab my hand! Come on, we're in. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.34,2:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快走  快走！  快！\N{\ren}Come on, let's go! Let's go, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.81,2:04:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\ren}Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.86,2:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 耶！   耶！   - 太好了！  漂亮！\N{\ren}- Yeah! Yeah! - All right! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.61,2:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 狗屎   - 大家都还好吗？\N{\ren}- Crap. - Everybody all right back there?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:05.37,2:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是的  宝贝！\N{\ren}Oh, yeah, baby!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.91,2:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-诺姆  你呢？    -没问题！\N{\ren}- Norm, you good? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.71,2:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉 我挨了一枪\N{\ren}This is gonna ruin my whole day.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.29,2:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格蕾丝中弹了！   - 什么？\N{\ren}- Grace is hit! - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.21,2:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快拿急救箱 - 急救箱！\N{\ren}- Get the trauma kit. - Trauma kit!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.88,2:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,压住伤口  格蕾丝\N{\ren}Keep the pressure on, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.63,2:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,急救箱在前面的舱壁上\N{\ren}Trauma kit's forward, on the bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.47,2:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格蕾丝  撑着点 - 不要紧  我没事\N{\ren}- Hang on, Grace. - Doesn't matter. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.31,2:05:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以了 - 吊起来吧！\N{\ren}- You're good to go. - Take it up!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.94,2:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,站稳了  我开始起吊了\N{\ren}Hold on. I'm pulling pitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.19,2:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题\N{\ren}You're clear!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.58,2:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一直向北飞  到深山里去\N{\ren}Just keep going north. Get us deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.41,2:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\ren}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.80,2:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,诺姆  你那里还好吗？\N{\ren}Norm, you all good up there?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.85,2:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  没问题\N{\ren}Yep! Still here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.97,2:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,至少他们无法跟踪我们到这儿来\N{\ren}Well, at least they can't track us up here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.66,2:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,至少到不了电磁旋涡这里\N{\ren}Not this far into the Vortex.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.72,2:06:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂树一带最强烈  对吗？\N{\ren}It's strongest at the Tree of Souls, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.85,2:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.43,2:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了  我们就去那里\N{\ren}Good. 'Cause that's where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.24,2:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼\N{\ren}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.78,2:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个大孩子\N{\ren}You big baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.58,2:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在转移\N{\ren}We're moving.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.58,2:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去找人救你  格蕾丝\N{\ren}I'm gonna get you some help, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.58,2:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是科学家  记得吗？\N{\ren}I'm a scientist, remember?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.67,2:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信童话故事\N{\ren}I don't believe in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:41.96,2:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会治好你的\N{\ren}The People can help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.34,2:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\ren}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.64,2:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要帮我们？\N{\ren}Why would they help us?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.53,2:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,纳威人说  艾娃会保护他们\N{\ren}The People say Eywa will provide.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.58,2:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没有家园  没有希望\N{\ren}With no home, no hope,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.33,2:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就只剩下一个地方可以去了\N{\ren}there was only one place they could go.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.93,2:07:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,准备就绪\N{\ren}Link's running.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.85,2:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰克  你有什么计划？   - 我没有计划\N{\ren}- What's the plan here, Jake? - There's no plan.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.89,2:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰现在是酋长了\N{\ren}Tsu'tey is Olo'eyktan now.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.12,2:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他是不会让你接近那里的\N{\ren}He's not gonna let you near that place.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.52,2:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我总得试试\N{\ren}I gotta try.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.70,2:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\N{\ren}Launching.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.51,2:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,放逐者\N{\ren}Outcast.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.51,2:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒\N{\ren}Betrayer.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.85,2:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,外星人\N{\ren}Alien.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.56,2:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里  没有任何地位\N{\ren}I was in the place the eye does not see.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.45,2:08:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要彼此的帮助\N{\ren}I needed their help, and they needed mine.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.24,2:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但要再度面对他们\N{\ren}But to ever face them again,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.29,2:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须重新改变他们对我的看法\N{\ren}I was gonna have to take it to a whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.34,2:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,人这一辈子有时就得靠一次疯狂的举动\N{\ren}Sometimes your whole life boils down to one insane move.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.43,2:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去做一件事\N{\ren}There's something we gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.89,2:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定不会喜欢的\N{\ren}You're not gonna like it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.61,2:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为  托鲁克是天上最可怕的飞兽\N{\ren}The way I had it figured, Toruk is the baddest cat in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.49,2:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没人敢攻击它\N{\ren}Nothing attacks him.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.66,2:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放松  兄弟\N{\ren}Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.45,2:09:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以它怎么会往上看呢？\N{\ren}So why would he ever look up?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.41,2:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这只是我的猜测\N{\ren}But that was just a theory.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.74,2:10:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,魅影骑士\N{\ren}Toruk Macto?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.15,2:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到你\N{\ren}I See you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.74,2:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到你\N{\ren}I See you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.37,2:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害怕  杰克\N{\ren}I was afraid, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:30.50,2:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为我的族人担心\N{\ren}For my people.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.05,2:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我不再害怕了\N{\ren}I'm not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:46.10,2:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰  阿特尤之子\N{\ren}Tsu'tey, son of Ateyo...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:49.06,2:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我站在你面前\N{\ren}...I stand before you...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.11,2:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,随时准备为奥玛蒂卡亚族效劳\N{\ren}...ready to serve the Omaticaya people.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.86,2:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是酋长  也是位伟大的战士\N{\ren}You are Olo'eyktan, and you are a great warrior.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:03.29,2:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我办不到\N{\ren}I can't do this without you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.50,2:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,魅影骑士\N{\ren}Toruk Macto,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.76,2:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意和你一起飞翔\N{\ren}I will fly with you.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.81,2:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友快死了\N{\ren}My friend is dying.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.94,2:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝快死了\N{\ren}Grace is dying.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.48,2:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求艾娃帮助她\N{\ren}I beg the help of Eywa.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.25,2:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们在哪里  格蕾丝\N{\ren}Look where we are, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.96,2:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我得采集一些样本\N{\ren}I need to take some samples.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.78,2:13:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾娃也许会选择保存她的灵魂\N{\ren}The Great Mother may choose to save all that she is
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.08,2:13:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,转移到这个身体\N{\ren}in this body.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.08,2:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这有可能吗\N{\ren}Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.83,2:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她必须通过艾娃之眼的考验  然后再回来\N{\ren}She must pass through the eye of Eywa and return.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.59,2:13:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  杰克.萨利\N{\ren}But, Jakesully,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.13,2:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她非常虚弱\N{\ren}she is very weak.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.22,2:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  格蕾丝 他们会把你治好的\N{\ren}Hang on, Grace. They're gonna fix you up.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.23,2:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,万灵之母  请倾听我们的祈祷\N{\ren}Hear us please, All Mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:54.40,2:13:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,救救她吧  艾娃\N{\ren}Eywa, help her.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.40,2:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们请您接收这个灵魂\N{\ren}Take this spirit into you...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.15,2:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,让她重回我们身边\N{\ren}...and breathe her back to us.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.20,2:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,让她的生命得以延续\N{\ren}Let her walk among us...
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.37,2:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以一个真正纳威人的身份活在我们之间\N{\ren}...as one of The People.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.28,2:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\ren}Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.78,2:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\ren}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.08,2:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到艾娃了  杰克\N{\ren}I'm with her, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.79,2:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她是真的！\N{\ren}She's real!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.21,2:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝？  格蕾丝  别  格蕾丝！\N{\ren}Grace? Grace, please. Grace!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:03.55,2:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\ren}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.13,2:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\ren}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.14,2:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝！\N{\ren}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.02,2:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝！\N{\ren}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.27,2:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？\N{\ren}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.15,2:15:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有用吗？\N{\ren}Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.24,2:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她的伤势太严重了  已经太迟了\N{\ren}Her wounds were too great. It was not enough time.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:38.00,2:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟艾娃在一起了\N{\ren}She is with Eywa now.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.54,2:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请你允许  我现在有话要说\N{\ren}With your permission, I will speak now.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.58,2:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,恳请你为我翻译\N{\ren}You would honor me by translating.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.13,2:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,天空人传达一个信息给我们\N{\ren}The Sky People have sent us a message
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.72,2:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以为所欲为\N{\ren}that they can take whatever they want
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.93,2:16:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都阻止不了\N{\ren}and no one can stop them.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:43.31,2:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们要传达一个信息给他们\N{\ren}Well, we will send them a message.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:47.74,2:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将乘着风而飞翔\N{\ren}You ride out as fast as the wind can carry you.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.37,2:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将集合全部的部落一同作战\N{\ren}You tell the other clans to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:58.87,2:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们魅影骑士在召唤他们\N{\ren}You tell them Toruk Macto calls to them.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.59,2:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就出发！\N{\ren}And you fly now with me!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:07.42,2:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟们  姐妹们\N{\ren}My brothers! Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:11.01,2:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要让天空人知道\N{\ren}And we will show the Sky People
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.10,2:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可以为所欲为\N{\ren}that they cannot take whatever they want,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.47,2:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里是\N{\ren}and that this,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.64,2:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的家园！\N{\ren}this is our land!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.78,2:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,出发！\N{\ren}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.33,2:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,出发！\N{\ren}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:15.16,2:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,出发！\N{\ren}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:34.05,2:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走遍世界各地\N{\ren}We rode out to the four winds.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.30,2:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在平原上找到了马族部落\N{\ren}To the horse clans of the plain.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.69,2:18:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,把他们赶回去\N{\ren}Back to the stars!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.81,2:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到东海岸边找到了伊卡兰族\N{\ren}To the ikran people ofthe Eastern Sea.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:47.06,2:18:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们的子孙后代\N{\ren}For our children's children!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.44,2:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,魅影骑士的召唤让所有人团结在一起\N{\ren}When Toruk Macto called them, they came.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.86,2:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发\N{\ren}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.40,2:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个基地的每个人\N{\ren}Everyone on this base, every one of you,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.99,2:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,都在为生存努力\N{\ren}is fighting for survival.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.90,2:19:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不争的事实！\N{\ren}That's a fact!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:39.24,2:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在外面有一大群纳威人正在集结\N{\ren}There's an aboriginal horde out there
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.28,2:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,准备攻击\N{\ren}massing for an attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:44.08,2:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,根据卫星照片显示\N{\ren}Now, these orbital images tell me
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.37,2:19:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这些纳威人  一天之内就从几百人\N{\ren}that the hostiles' numbers have gone from a few hundred
Dialogue: 0,2:19:51.63,2:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,增加到两千多人\N{\ren}to well over 2,000 in one day.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.76,2:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而且人数还在增加当中\N{\ren}And more are pouring in.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.22,2:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一周后  将会达到两万人\N{\ren}In a week's time, there could be 20,000 of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.72,2:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那时  他们会冲破我们的外围防线\N{\ren}At that point, they will overrun our perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:05.10,2:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不会让这种事情发生\N{\ren}Well, that's not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.94,2:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唯一的办法就是先发制人\N{\ren}Our only security lies in pre-emptive attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.61,2:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将以其人之道还治其人之身\N{\ren}We will fight terror with terror.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.32,2:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那些纳威人相信他们的家园\N{\ren}Now, the hostiles believe that this mountain stronghold of theirs
Dialogue: 0,2:20:23.58,2:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,受到了他们的\N{\ren}is protected by their...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.00,2:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的神灵保佑\N{\ren}Their deity.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:28.71,2:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么当我们摧毁它的时候\N{\ren}And when we destroy it,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.83,2:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在他们的记忆里深深的烙上一个教训\N{\ren}we will blast a crater in their racial memory so deep
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.29,2:20:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们永远再也不敢接近\N{\ren}that they won't come
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.97,2:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,离这里方圆一千公里的地方\N{\ren}within 1,000 klicks of this place ever again.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.88,2:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,而这件事也将成为不变的事实\N{\ren}And that, too, is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.30,2:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错\N{\ren}Yeah! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:52.52,2:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  这里很夸张  几乎全体总动员\N{\ren}Jake, it's crazy here. It's full mobilization.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.00,2:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要把飞行器变成轰炸机\N{\ren}They're rigging the shuttle as a bomber.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.57,2:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在运输船上装满了大堆\N{\ren}They've got these huge pallets
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.74,2:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,用来炸矿坑用专用的炸药\N{\ren}of mine explosives.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.90,2:21:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,准备用来摧毁什么\N{\ren}It's for some kind of shock-and-awe campaign.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.91,2:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人全都疯了\N{\ren}Fricking daisy cutters!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.33,2:21:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,夸奇上校接管一切\N{\ren}Quaritch has taken over.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.30,2:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在全部都听他号令  谁也没办法阻止他\N{\ren}He's rolling, and there's no stopping him.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.25,2:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么时候开始！    -明天早上六点\N{\ren}- When?  - 06:00 tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.42,2:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 麦克斯！  麦克斯！    - 我不能再说了\N{\ren}- Max! Max!  - I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:14.17,2:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们玩完了\N{\ren}We're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.13,2:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我原先还以为能有个什么计划\N{\ren}And I was hoping for some sort of tactical plan
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.38,2:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能够全身而退的\N{\ren}that didn't involve martyrdom.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:23.09,2:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用弓箭对抗武装飞机\N{\ren}We're going up against gunships with bows and arrows.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.48,2:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在外面有十五个部落\N{\ren}I have 15 clans out there.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.19,2:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,超过两千名战士\N{\ren}That's over 2,000 warriors.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.82,2:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们清楚这些山的地形\N{\ren}Now, we know these mountains.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:37.54,2:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都清楚  你也清楚  但他们不熟悉\N{\ren}We fly them. You fly them. They don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.32,2:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的电子设备在这里不管用\N{\ren}Their instruments won't work up here.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.75,2:21:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,自动追踪导弹也没有用\N{\ren}Missile tracking won't work.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.87,2:21:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只能手动瞄准\N{\ren}They'll have to fire a line of sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.45,2:21:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们攻过来  我们就有地形上的优势\N{\ren}If they bring the fight to us, then we have the home-field advantage.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.58,2:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他肯定会直接轰炸灵魂之树的\N{\ren}You know he's gonna commit that bomber straight to the Tree of Souls.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:57.13,2:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我知道\N{\ren}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:58.38,2:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果让他们到达那里  那就玩完了\N{\ren}If they get to the Tree of Souls, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.01,2:22:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是纳威人跟艾娃  他们先灵联系的地方\N{\ren}That's their direct line to Eywa, their ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.01,2:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这会毁了纳威人意志\N{\ren}It'll destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.05,2:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们最好别让他们得逞\N{\ren}Then I guess we'd better stop him.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.57,2:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能只是在和一棵树说话\N{\ren}I'm probably just talking to a tree right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:29.99,2:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果您真的在那里 我必须提醒您\N{\ren}But if you're there, I need to give you a heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.29,2:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果格蕾丝和您在一起 请您看一看她的记忆\N{\ren}If Grace is with you, look into her memories.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:42.97,2:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我们来的那个世界\N{\ren}See the world we come from.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:46.18,2:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那里已经没有绿色的大地了\N{\ren}There's no green there.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.47,2:22:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们亲手杀死了自己的母亲\N{\ren}They killed their Mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:52.27,2:22:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们要在这里做同样的事\N{\ren}And they're gonna do the same here.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:56.40,2:22:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的天空人会来到这里\N{\ren}More Sky People are gonna come.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.07,2:23:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只会越来越多  而且永远不会停止\N{\ren}They're gonna come like a rain that never ends.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:03.40,2:23:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们能阻止他们\N{\ren}Unless we stop them.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.74,2:23:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道您选择了我是有原因的\N{\ren}Look, you chose me for something.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.29,2:23:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会奋起抗争\N{\ren}I will stand and fight.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.21,2:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道我会这样做的\N{\ren}You know I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:19.29,2:23:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但我真的需要您的帮助\N{\ren}But I need a little help here.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:27.68,2:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾娃是不会偏袒任何一边的  杰克\N{\ren}Our Great Mother does not take sides, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.52,2:23:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她只维护生态的平衡\N{\ren}She protects only the balance of life.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.78,2:23:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我总得试一试\N{\ren}It was worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:20.19,2:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对！  对！  这就是我要的!\N{\ren}Yeah! Yeah! That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.23,2:24:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对！  对！  这就是我要的  伙计！\N{\ren}Yeah! Yeah! That's what I'm talking about, man!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.71,2:24:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是指挥机  我们将进入电磁漩涡了\N{\ren}This is Group Leader. We are entering the Flux Vortex.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:41.46,2:24:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,切换到手动飞行模式\N{\ren}Switch to manual flight mode.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:43.25,2:24:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  手动飞行模式\N{\ren}Copy. Manual flight mode.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.96,2:25:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我是总指挥官\N{\ren}This is Papa Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:21.92,2:25:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我要这次任务速战速决  我赶着回家吃晚饭\N{\ren}I want this mission high and tight. I want to be home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.51,2:25:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,机甲小组  出发\N{\ren}Suit Team, go.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:33.99,2:25:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  姑娘们  给他们好看吧\N{\ren}All right, ladies, let's bring the pain!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.82,2:25:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,行动  行动  行动\N{\ren}Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.07,2:25:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,B1-1  向左移动\N{\ren}Bravo 1-1, move left.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.41,2:25:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,B1-1  向左移动  注意侧翼\N{\ren}Bravo 1-1 moving left. Watch flank.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:02.16,2:26:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保持队形  继续前进 - 收到\N{\ren}- Watch formation. Keep moving.  - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:05.79,2:26:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,C2-1  注意保持距离\N{\ren}Charlie 2-1, watch your spacing.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.30,2:26:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  完毕\N{\ren}Copy that. Over.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.67,2:26:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看上面  注意上方  注意热能雷达\N{\ren}Eyes up. Check that overhead. And watch those thermal scans.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:14.97,2:26:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫所有单位  指挥官在领队发令\N{\ren}All call signs, Papa has lead,
Dialogue: 0,2:26:17.54,2:26:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,向目标推进\N{\ren}pushing to target.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.35,2:26:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,护卫机  紧紧跟着我的航天飞机\N{\ren}Escorts, stay close on my shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.90,2:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在这我们会刮掉一些油漆的\N{\ren}We are gonna lose some paint in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.40,2:26:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,机枪小组  注意山边峭壁\N{\ren}Gun crews, keep your head on a swivel.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.15,2:26:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别大意  各位  他们就在附近\N{\ren}Make no mistake, people, they're out there.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:36.66,2:26:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  各位  目标出现 距离四公里\N{\ren}All right, people, target in sight. Range, four klicks.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:39.99,2:26:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,女战神1-6号  准备投弹\N{\ren}Valkyrie 1-6, get your payload ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.33,2:26:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,了解  准备发射\N{\ren}Copy. Prepare to offload.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:43.69,2:26:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,参谋中士  炸弹就位\N{\ren}Staff Sergeant, stage the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.62,2:26:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,推到舷梯上!  快点!\N{\ren}Roll it to the ramp! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.09,2:26:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,停!\N{\ren}Hold!
Dialogue: 0,2:26:59.18,2:27:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,C2-1  动作快点\N{\ren}Charlie 2-1, got big movement.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:01.31,2:27:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保持不动  - 等等  等等\N{\ren}- Hold position. - Hold up, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:02.81,2:27:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,五百公尺处有动静\N{\ren}We got movement out there, 500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.89,2:27:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,C2-1  保持不动\N{\ren}Charlie 2-1, hold position.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.07,2:27:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  地面有状况   正在快速接近\N{\ren}Sir, ground has movement! Fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:16.07,2:27:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 指挥机  这是骑士小队 - 成射击阵型!\N{\ren}- Charlie Oscar, Rider section. - Firing line!
Dialogue: 0,2:27:19.03,2:27:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,目标接近中  距离四百公尺\N{\ren}Targets closing. Range, 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.45,2:27:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能把这个弄清楚点吗?\N{\ren}Can't you clean it up?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.74,2:27:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  长官  有电磁波干扰\N{\ren}No, sir. It's the Flux.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:53.48,2:27:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟  我杀条路进去  你跟在我后面\N{\ren}Brother, I'm gonna punch a hole. You follow me through.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.90,2:28:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所有战机  自主射击!  自主射击!\N{\ren}All aircraft, weapons free! Weapons free!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.78,2:28:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,右转  掉头\N{\ren}Break right. Come around.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.54,2:28:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,轰掉他们!\N{\ren}Light them up!
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.67,2:28:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,分散队形  全面攻击敌人\N{\ren}Break formation, engage all hostiles.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.14,2:29:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我子弹吧!\N{\ren}Yeah! Get some!
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.01,2:29:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,蝎子炮艇机  扫荡敌人\N{\ren}Scorpions, pursue and destroy.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:58.69,2:30:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克?  杰克  听得到吗?\N{\ren}Jake! Jake! You copy?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.15,2:30:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要撤退了!  敌人火力太猛!\N{\ren}We're falling back! We're getting hammered!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.86,2:30:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  赶快离开\N{\ren}Copy. Get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:10.04,2:30:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他  快给我追!\N{\ren}That's him. Get after him!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:28.39,2:30:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他!\N{\ren}Take him out!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:38.19,2:30:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把她轰了!\N{\ren}Light her up!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.66,2:30:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把她轰了\N{\ren}Right there!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.20,2:30:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是只有你才有枪  混蛋\N{\ren}You're not the only one with a gun, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:52.71,2:30:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看住她  - 全部瞄准她\N{\ren}- Keep her in your sights. - Purging. Feeding the leak.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:54.42,2:30:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全力攻击她\N{\ren}Arming all pods.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:01.21,2:31:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像话!\N{\ren}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:32.95,2:31:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,西子\N{\ren}Seyzey!
Dialogue: 0,2:32:38.02,2:32:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,淘气鬼一号中弹  我要返航了\N{\ren}Rogue One is hit. I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:41.15,2:32:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  抱歉\N{\ren}Sorry, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:59.58,2:33:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\N{\ren}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:18.77,2:33:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,苏泰   兄弟  你听得到吗?\N{\ren}Tsu'tey! Brother, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:24.11,2:33:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,淘气鬼一号  你收得到吗?\N{\ren}Rogue One, you copy?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:27.78,2:33:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,楚迪!\N{\ren}Trudy!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:39.83,2:33:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,两分钟后抵达目标\N{\ren}Time to target, two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:41.46,2:33:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,女战神1-6号  障碍已清除  准备开火\N{\ren}Valkyrie 1-6, you are cleared and hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:43.96,2:33:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,收到  飞龙号  开始投弹程序\N{\ren}Copy, Dragon. We are starting our bomb run.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:51.97,2:33:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一号弹  解除保险!\N{\ren}Arm number one!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.03,2:33:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一号弹  保险已解除!\N{\ren}Number one armed!
Dialogue: 0,2:33:57.18,2:33:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克!\N{\ren}Ma Jake!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:00.35,2:34:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我听得到\N{\ren}I read you.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:10.65,2:34:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妮特丽 - 西子死了\N{\ren}- Neytiri! - Seyzey's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:13.24,2:34:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人离得很近  人非常多\N{\ren}They are very close. They are many.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:17.16,2:34:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要攻击\N{\ren}Do not attack.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:19.24,2:34:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了吗?  妮特丽\N{\ren}Do you read me, Neytiri?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.79,2:34:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要攻击\N{\ren}Do not attack!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:25.42,2:34:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快点撤退  现在就离开  这是命令\N{\ren}Fall back now. Get out of there! That's an order!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:36.68,2:34:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,妮特丽!\N{\ren}Neytiri!
Dialogue: 0,2:34:39.97,2:34:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,前方有动静  有动静\N{\ren}I got movement, I got movement.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:41.98,2:34:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,留在原地  有东西来了\N{\ren}Hold position. Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:44.31,2:34:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B1-1  有很大的感应  注意屏幕\N{\ren}Bravo 1-1, I got a big seating.Turn screens over.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:46.19,2:34:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西靠近了  距离两百米\N{\ren}We got movement 200 meters.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:47.85,2:34:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,保持队形\N{\ren}Hold your formation.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.40,2:34:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好  - 注意侧翼\N{\ren}- Be ready. - Watch your flanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:55.28,2:34:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,距离一百公尺  快速接近中\N{\ren}Hundred meters and closing fast.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:13.34,2:35:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得离开这里!\N{\ren}We gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:22.72,2:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 撤退!  撤退!   - 快撤!  快撤!  快撤!\N{\ren}- Fall back! Fall back! - Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:24.52,2:35:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退!  快跑!  快跑!\N{\ren}Fall back! On the run! On the run!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.07,2:35:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克  艾娃听到了\N{\ren}Jake, Eywa has heard you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:43.66,2:35:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,艾娃听到你了!\N{\ren}Eywa has heard you!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:56.01,2:35:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.69,2:36:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退!  快撤!  快撤!\N{\ren}Fall back! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.05,2:36:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  护卫机不是被击落就是正在撤退\N{\ren}Sir! All escorts are down or falling back.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:38.76,2:36:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,来结束这一切吧 飞龙号呼叫女战神1-6号\N{\ren}Let's get this done. Valkyrie 1-6, this is Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:42.97,2:36:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 强攻目标 - 收到  强攻目标\N{\ren}- Press to target. - Copy. Pressing to target.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:45.89,2:36:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,投弹倒计时三十秒\N{\ren}Stand by to drop, 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:07.75,2:37:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,听我指令  二  一  投弹\N{\ren}On my mark. Two, one, mark.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:10.25,2:37:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,投弹！  投弹！  投弹！  快  快  快  快\N{\ren}Drop! Drop! Drop! Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:12.58,2:37:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,投弹！  投弹！  投弹！  快  快  快  快\N{\ren}Drop! Drop! Drop! Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:46.74,2:37:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,顶住！\N{\ren}Brace!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:04.93,2:38:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是萨利\N{\ren}It's Sully.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:19.99,2:38:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 戴上滤气面罩！ - 破裂警报！\N{\ren}- Mask on!  - Breach alarm!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:06.65,2:41:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊  到爸爸这里来\N{\ren}Come on. Come to papa.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:35.97,2:41:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧！  夸奇\N{\ren}Give it up, Quaritch!
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.81,2:41:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都结束了\N{\ren}It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:43.56,2:41:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一口气在就不会结束\N{\ren}Nothing's over while I'm breathing.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:46.11,2:41:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这话正合我意\N{\ren}I kind of hoped you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:44.54,2:42:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧！\N{\ren}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:43:01.64,2:43:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  萨利  背叛自己的种族感觉怎样？\N{\ren}Hey, Sully, how's it feel to betray your own race?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:10.40,2:43:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以为你是他们的一份子？\N{\ren}You think you're one of them?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:13.82,2:43:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,该醒来了\N{\ren}Time to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:59.68,2:45:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克？\N{\ren}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.44,2:45:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\ren}Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:33.54,2:45:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\ren}Jake.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:50.98,2:45:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克   我的杰克！\N{\ren}Jake! Ma Jake!
Dialogue: 0,2:46:34.65,2:46:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到你\N{\ren}I See you.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:41.57,2:46:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到你\N{\ren}I See you.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:08.01,2:47:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到你   兄弟\N{\ren}I See you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:10.43,2:47:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,族人安全了吗\N{\ren}Are The People safe?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:14.48,2:47:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们安全了\N{\ren}They're safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:22.11,2:47:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\ren}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,2:47:24.78,2:47:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能领导他们了\N{\ren}I cannot lead The People.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:27.57,2:47:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你必需要领导他们 杰克萨利\N{\ren}You must lead them... Jakesully.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:31.29,2:47:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是当首领的料\N{\ren}I'm not officer material.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:33.29,2:47:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这是注定的\N{\ren}It is decided.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.38,2:47:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\ren}Now...
Dialogue: 0,2:47:40.80,2:47:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,完成奥玛蒂卡亚族该做的事吧\N{\ren}...do the duty of Olo'eyktan.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:47.80,2:47:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀你的\N{\ren}I will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:49.51,2:47:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了\N{\ren}It is the way!
Dialogue: 0,2:47:53.47,2:47:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这对于我来说是最好的\N{\ren}And it is good.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:57.31,2:47:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会永远记得的\N{\ren}I will be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:01.77,2:48:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我与....魅影骑士一起战斗过！\N{\ren}I fought... with Toruk Macto!
Dialogue: 0,2:48:08.32,2:48:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们还是兄弟\N{\ren}And we were brothers.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:11.62,2:48:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是....我曾经的最终幻影\N{\ren}And he... was my last shadow.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:02.13,2:49:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,外星人返回他们垂死的星球\N{\ren}The aliens went back to their dying world.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:07.13,2:49:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只有少数人被允许留下\N{\ren}Only a few were chosen to stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:22.27,2:49:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,苦难的时代终于结束了\N{\ren}The time of great sorrow was ending.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:26.86,2:49:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不再需要魅影骑士了\N{\ren}Toruk Macto was no longerneeded.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:41.83,2:49:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我想这应该是我最后一次的影像日记了\N{\ren}Well, I guess this is my last video log.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:47.55,2:49:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不论今晚发生什么  总之\N{\ren}'Cause whatever happens tonight, either way, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,2:49:52.39,2:49:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不会再回到这里了\N{\ren}I'm not gonna be coming back to this place.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:58.85,2:50:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我该走了\N{\ren}Well, I guess I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:03.56,2:50:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想错过我的派对\N{\ren}Yeah, I don't want to be late for my own party.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:09.94,2:50:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟  今天是我的生日\N{\ren}Yeah, it's my birthday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,2:50:14.91,2:50:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是杰克.萨利  录影完毕\N{\ren}This is Jake Sully signing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:10.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────\N电影中地球上的人类身陷有毒废料、饥饿、贫穷 人口亦已达到可\N怕的200亿在人类文明的挤压下 地球已不堪重负正逐渐走向衰亡\N─────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N即使是月球的背面 也被星罗棋布的人类城市灯火所点亮 人口过剩 过\N度开发 核武恐怖主义 环境战争 发电厂和废料堆中的放射性物质泄露\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:30.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\N有毒的工业垃圾 空气污染 滥砍滥伐 海洋污染与过度捕捞 全球\N变暖臭氧层消失 物种灭绝等等 这一切都令曾经绿意盎然的地球\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────\N看起来跟化粪池已没什么两样 海洋也因为过度捕捞已经贫瘠\N有毒废水不断流入 令所有鲸鱼以及至少一半的鱼类已经绝迹\N───────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────\N在陆地上 跟本世纪初相比 半数以上的动植物种已经消失\N剩下的也大多濒临灭绝 人类利用科技上的优势得以继续生存\N───────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:02:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────\N但人类已远离自然世界 大自然已经被摧残的千疮百孔\N国家公园不复存在 取而代之的是住宅区和蛋白质农场\N────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:10.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N例如 昔日的约塞米特国家公园已被开发成高级公寓区 多数沿海区域已\N变成藻类养殖场 因为现在只有螺旋藻可以满足如此庞大人口的食物需要\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────\N日常食品已蜕变为藻类浓缩蛋白与各种香料的怪异搭配\N天啊！这样的生活真的会到来吗？！\N────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:04:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────────────\N“RDA”全称是Resources.Development.Administration 即“资源开发管理同盟”\N是人类社会中最大的非政府组织 经营范围包括采矿、运输、药品、武器和通讯等方面\N──────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────────────\NRDA已经比绝大多数的地球上的政府还要强大 对于潘多拉以及其他地外星球 都具有垄断性\N的开发和运输权利 这是由ICA（“星际商业管理组织” — 类似于现在的欧盟）授权给RDA的\N─────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────\N根据《国际太空资源开发公约》等协议 RDA不得拥有大规模杀伤性武器（如激\N光武器、纳米武器、生物武器、核武器等） 其军事力量的使用也受到很大限制\N───────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:05:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────\N短短几十年 RDA已发展成为一个商业巨头 推动并建立了遍布世界的高速\N磁悬浮列车“捷运”系统（速度极快,45分钟可以从纽约抵达巴黎） 而这\N种列车需要大量的超导材料即潘多拉星球的超导矿石  才能保证持续运营\N─────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\N许多环境组织和科学家已经对RDA无限制开采超导矿石提出了反对意\N见 称其正在对潘多拉星球的生态系统造成严重且不可逆转的伤害\N但是 要求ICA收回RDA对潘多拉独家开采权的上诉被无数次的驳回\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\N低温休眠（Cryosleep） 自从人体冷冻技术被成功实现以来 这种\N伟大的发明便在人类航天事业掀起革命 有了这种技术 人类能突破\N时间的障碍 让机体保持原状 人体在低温休眠舱里不需要食物和水\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:06:10.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────────\N低温休眠能让人在漫长的太空旅行中保持年轻 从低温休眠舱醒来时人们通常相当迷\N惑和非常不舒服 有些人醒来时甚至可能会恶心和极度虚弱 这是低温休眠的副作用\N─────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:29.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────────\N在冰冻状态下 宇宙射线造成的损伤不能随着新陈代谢修复 其危害可能会持续积累\N在复苏之后一次性的体现出来 如果航行时间达到百年以上 积累的辐射剂量可能造\N成急性放射病 解决这个问题 需要比飞船更厚重的辐射屏蔽材料 甚至是磁场护盾\N─────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────────────\N“创业之星”全称为星级货运航母“创业之星”（Interstellar.Vehicle.ISV.Venture.Star）\N编号为601-09 星级货运航母是往返于地球和潘多拉星之间的星际货运平台 用于把人员、建筑\N材料、设备输送到潘多拉星 再带回返回的人员和加工后的精矿Unobtanium（以后称其为超导矿石）\N───────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:07:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N潘多拉星环绕这一颗巨大而璀璨的星球 那便是被地球人以希腊神话里的\N独眼巨人命名为“波里菲密斯（Polyphemis）” 阿尔法星系有三颗恒星\N分别是阿尔法A、阿尔法B、阿尔法C 波里菲密斯就绕著阿尔法A星运转\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:10.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────\N创业之星长1600多米 宽330米 高218.5米 货运能力350吨\N巡航速度为每秒210000公里（相当于光速的70%）\N───────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────────\N速度数据看上去很快 但从地球到潘多拉星球仍需要飞行六年多的时间 它的驱动\N系统包括两台反物质湮灭能动力引擎 一座光子风帆 一台核聚变星际巡航引擎\N────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:30.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────────\N“瓦尔基里”航天飞机（The.Valjyrie.Shuttle) 长101.73米 宽80.03米, 高8.0米\N在大气层内最高速度3马赫 一次能运载多达60名武装士兵 25吨货物 具有垂直起降功\N能 能够平稳的着陆 还能在潘多拉星的母星---波吕斐摩斯大气中采集氢气 作为燃料\N───────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N“瓦尔基里”安装有强大的反物质引擎使他不需要助推火箭就可以在大气\N层内和外层空间中自由飞行 它是“创业之星”与潘多拉之间的唯一运输\N工具 它最重要的用途就是把开采加工后的超导矿石运上“创业之星”\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────\N过滤面罩(Exopack) 是人类在潘多拉星球上的必须佩带的装备\N由一个透明的面罩和一个过滤空气的装置组成 潘多拉星的大气\N中充满有毒气体 必须经过简单的过滤才能直接被人类所呼吸\N────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:08:05.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\N地狱之门（Hell's.Gate）基地的官方名称是“资源开发管理局太阳\N系外殖民地-01” 它是地球人在潘多拉星上殖民活动的基地 其由\N于身处有毒的环境和危险生物的包围之中 所以被称为“地狱之门”\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:12.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N斗轮挖掘机（Bucket.Wheel.Excavator） 是RDA在潘多拉最大的机器\N它具有巨型齿壮轮子 能像嚼在岩石表面一样紧紧地抓住岩面 由聚变\N反应堆和太阳能混合提供动力 斗轮挖掘机里面有一个大型气密控制室\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:12.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────────\N地狱卡车（Hell.Truck）是RDA用来运输矿石回到地狱之门以及用来运输各种物品的工具\N运输的超导矿石的土壤或岩石 由于超导矿石的迈斯纳效应 负载略有浮动 更易于运输\N───────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:22.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────\N四架SA-52B“毒蝎”式武装炮艇机(Scorpion.Gunship)护卫航天飞机降落基地\N───────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:32.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────\N地狱之门基地完全是按战区基地级别进行警戒\N────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:09:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────────────────\N安全营运组织(Security.Operations)简称SecOps 是地球上的一个非政府组织 主要工作是\N在世界各地执行安保工作 RDA与其签定了长期协议 为在潘多拉星球的各项活动提供安全保证\N──────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\NSecOps不断向潘多拉输送人员 其中很多是退伍军人 为了限制其军\N事实力 ICA禁止SecOps使用大规模杀伤性武器以及各种先进的装备\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N这就解释为什么在人类已经可以星际旅行的年代 在潘多拉的SecOps还在\N使用发射子弹的枪支 连把激光枪都没有 事实上 收钱驻防在潘多拉星\N的SecOps就连基础军备都是从旧货市场淘来的旧货 甚至是旧货中的旧货\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:46.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────\NSecOps使用的各式装备都是21世纪末生产的古董\N真TMD给地球人丢脸！没办法谁叫ICA这么规定的\N─────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:10:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────────────\NSecOps状态最好的AMP单人操作的中型动力外骨骼系统（Amplified.Mobility.Platform）\N也是RDA拿20年前的设计图纸 花了些钱重开生产线生产的一批淘汰货\N────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:12.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────\N地狱之门（Hell's.Gate）基地的SecOps士兵 主要装备GS-221.BCU模块化步枪\N───────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:25.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────\N地狱卡车的轮子非常大和厚实 需要液压动力协助转向 轻松通过潘多拉的\N各种地形 抵御潘多拉各种生物威胁 卡车上设有装甲 但大和锋利的物体\N或重火力还是可以穿透它的 卡车上还有摄像头 能使司机时刻留意周围\N─────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:35.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────────────\N基地SecOps指挥官上校的手枪型号是SN-9.WASP黄蜂转轮手枪 并使用超高速9毫米穿甲弹\N────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:11:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────────\N曾有个善待动物组织花费了120万美元投放了广告 广告上一个饥饿垂死的纳\N威族女人手持着强烈谴责RDA行为的标语 这组广告在人类社会中产生了强烈\N的反响 吸引了世界的广泛关注 并使得人们对ICA授权RDA提出了更多的谴责\N──────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N但是！稍后这个广告内容被发现时伪造的 这使得世界对善待动物组织\N提出了谴责 这个被称作“猫女”的事件 使得很多国家提出了要求广\N告真实的法案 随后美国通过了类似的法案 这真是有阴谋就有黑幕！\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:47.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────\N杰克.萨利回到似曾相识的军营 很享受这种气氛\N──────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:11.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N生命研究室(The.Biolab)是地狱之门内设的一个重要部门 主要负责研\N究潘多拉的生态 生物 也为RDA采矿人员以及各项活动提供技术协助\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:21.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────\N生命研究室工作包括提供医疗保健服务 培育潘多拉可食用性动\N植物等 当然最重要的 生命研究室是进行阿凡达链接的场所\N────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:32.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N阿凡达计划先提取纳威人的DNA 再从地球人中选出志愿者 接着在地\N球上的RDA遗传实验室里 培育出混合纳威人和地球人DNA的体外胚胎\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:42.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────\N在运往潘多拉的3年（相当于地球上的5年）旅途中 胚胎在人工\N培育下成长为近乎成人的大小（这事因为纳威人的成长速度较快）\N─────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:13:02.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N当克隆体成长为一个完整的”纳威人”后 人类志愿者便可通过精神联络\N系统（Psionic.Link.Unit）让自己的意识进驻其中 就像操作自己的身\N体一样与这个克隆体合二为一 化身为在这个星球上自由活动的伪纳威人\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:12.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────\N然而并不是任何人都可以操纵这个克隆纳威人 只有\NDNA与他身上人类DNA配型相符的人才有这样的能力\N───────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:32.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────\N在链接后 宿主将活在“阿凡达”中 通过“阿凡达”去感知这个世\N界 阿凡达和纳威人生理结构基本一样 他们的肌肉组织强度是人类\N的四倍 神经元高度发达 骨骼中碳元素以高强度化合物形式存在\N──────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:47.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────────\N最初 阿凡达计划的目的是为了创造出不需要环境保护装置即可在外作业的\N矿工 当然还有应对潘多拉星球本地的危险的士兵 这才是最有价值的部分\N─────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:14:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N然而 过于昂贵的精神联络系统没法满足量产的需要 阿凡达单体造价\N为50亿美元 根据官方设定的通货膨胀率 约合2008年币值37亿美元\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:18.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────\N“阿凡达”现在最主要被应用于和纳威人的沟通交流 研究纳威\N人和潘多拉的生态系统 当然也有作给纳威人洗脑 教授他们地\N球人类的文化等 好让他们同化 以便服从人类在潘星采矿\N────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:15:05.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────\N大姐！不是...大妈！外面的纳威人也算是异形 要不您拿上枪出去撸纳威人吧！\N───────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────\N潘多拉超导矿石的性能超越了所有人类曾经制造出的超导体\N它可在1516摄氏度（华氏2716度）的状态下保持超导性能\N──────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:17:05.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────────────\N超导矿同时有具有超强的抗磁性能 即使放在10亿高斯（10万特斯拉）强度的\N磁场内依然能保持超导性能不变 这比地球上任何一种物质都要强1000倍以上\N──────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:25.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────────────\N科学家认为 数十亿年前 当半人马座阿尔法A卫星系统在从原始宇宙尘埃中产生时 一颗\N火星大小的天体撞击了还处于原始熔岩状态的潘多拉星球 其镍铁合金核心被四分五裂\N────────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N这种远超人类技术能力的撞击产生了超高温和超高压 与周围行星的磁\N场引起互动反应 从而为超导矿这种独特物质的产生创造了有利条件\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:53.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N超导矿精炼产品的在地球市场价值达到每公斤8位数的美元（利润太大）\N这对地球经济的发展具有极其重要的影响！资本家也是无利吃苦的啊！\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:20.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────\N纳威人把“阿凡达”这种克隆纳威人叫做Uniltirantokx\N也就是梦游者（Dreamwalker）的意思\N─────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:18:15.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────\N羊水箱（Amnio.tank）用于体外克隆纳威人 肢体和器官的培育的仪器\N长385.82厘米 148.4厘米宽 拥有近6350升的液体 被设计成可便携\N───────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:30.00,Note,,0,0,0,,─────────────────────────────\N纳威人是潘多拉星球上的土著 身高将近3米 令人惊讶的是 在\N许多方面 纳威人身体几乎是像人类一样（甚至人类的标准美丽）\N─────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,────────────────────────────────\N纳威人除了头上看起来像是一条黑色的辫子的东西以外身上没有任何毛发\N它称为Queue 是外露连接神经系统 潘多拉上的所有生物都有这个构造\N────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:50.00,Note,,0,0,0,,───────────────────────────────────────\N纳威人腰部狭窄 拉长 肩膀很宽 形成一个V型的背部！很到是符合某些二次元的审美！\N───────────────────────────────────────
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:21:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,──────────────────────────\N纳威人的颈部像猫头鹰一样灵活 几乎能180度旋转 每个\N纳威人身上的花纹都有两种 一种类似斑马条纹遍布全身\N──────────────────────────
